\id ACT
\h Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi
\mt1 Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®ghar
\imt1 Ufhuragh…®v…®ra zuira akamambaaŇč
\ip Kha mb…®ghar, a Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasir iŇčaari. Luk os…®risiir akamna aghuuŇč iti. Luk nomb…®ra kha mb…®gharo os…®ri. Kha mb…®ghar ee aŇčn garima, Got…®n…® utum…® utuav…®n Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasir kh…®vasima mee Iesus…®na akamana aghuuŇč Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuu ko Judian distrigh koma Samarian distrigh…®n gua ma unuuagh…®nana as…®siive bara andagha arui. (N…®…® Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®gharan 1.8…®n akaman gan.)
\ip Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®gharan khav a Isesus…®n phuesi gumasi rako amisir niazi, mee Judarira ar…®ghan aŇčga amuima a gua ikhevighava atamtam…®ra kha unuagh…®nan guu. A fhom…®ra Got…®m mb…®kemisir akama r…®Ňčg…®ran IsraeliiŇčn gumasi rako amisi v…®kemi. Luk ivh…®ra Krais…®n iŇčaari rako othevir men kh…®vtima, mee aŇčn gin maŇčaŇčga.
\ip Bighan ikh…®van mav, Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®ghar kamagh aŇčm mb…®kemi. AŇčga Got…®n…® utuman gamgaaŇčn iŇčari. A Got…®n…® Utum. Petekos…®n…® uthughun Got…®n…® utuum…® ufhuaraghav…®ra Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasighi iz…®va. Gumaghun Got…®n…® utum meen n…®gh…®n…®s…®gh …®raghava gamgaaŇč meŇčga an…®…®Ňči.
\ip Kha mb…®gharana avhen Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi, Iesusa amuisiri iŇčaarira rakoma ana akamana aghuuŇč gun gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčgeeghi.
\ip Ee thigira gumasi rako amisir avh…®rar garima, mee akamana aghuuŇčn khav…®ra g…®n zuima, akaman khav…®ra aghavagharan Got…®n gumasi rakoma amisigha an…®…®ndi. Mb…®sevisi gumasi mb…®ghar, mb…®sevi gumasira avh…®rara niazi. Pita ri Pol…®n niaghasira bar avh…®re ikevi.
\ip Pita ufhuaraghavh…®ra Iesus ane mb…®sevisima an aŇčn g…®a aruisi gumagh. Pol…® ufhuaragha Iesus…®n g…®a aruisi phat…®. A Iesus…®n akamam ba oraghava aŇčn g…®n zui gumasi rako amisira afharavaghaousua bar aghavaghari. Kamagh amuisima Iesus Pol…®n d…®…®sima a thighira bar aŇčn…® ufharasiri iŇčaaran gumaghava kha mb…®gharana avhen iti os…®…®rir marsi.
\ip Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasiri IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®gharana avhen…®m mb…®zeer marsi kamagh…®usue, ‚Äúee‚ÄĚ iti. Gumasira avh…®rara kamaghi n…®ghh…®si Luk Pol…®n phorughava utisir marsira arui, a mamagha amuigha kamagh…®usue, ‚Äúee‚ÄĚ. Ma uthughun Luk ti Pol…®n g…®n gua Filipain…® uŇčuun thughat…®ghava a Filipain…® uŇčuun iti, mamagha amuigha Pol Filipain…® uŇčuua thaegha gusima akaman khuaŇč ‚Äúee‚ÄĚ nomthegha iti phat…®. (N…®…® Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®gharan 16.40…®n akaman gan.)
\c 1
\ms1 Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi Jerusalem…®na avhen Iesus…®na akam…® ukuri
\mr (Sapta 1.1--8.3)
\s1 Iesus…®n akama r…®Ňčg…®r kamagh…®usue, a Got…®n…® Utum ana amaaŇčgami
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Lu 1.1-4\xt Mk 16.19; Lu 24.49-51\x* Tiofilas, kh…®…® n…®…®m…®usua mb…®gharan khav ana os…®ri. Nan…® ufhuarasir…® mb…®gharan avhen, kh…®…® Iesus bar amuisi bisi, koma a gumasi rako amisir surea amuisi tharsi ivh…®rama anda os…®ri. Uthughun khav…®n Iesus…® r…®kavhigha non iŇčaarigha amua mamagh…®re ikha, gua a Got…®n…® uŇčuun guavanambosir…® uthughun uthusi bisi, kh…®…® anda os…®ri. Iesus a thighar Got…®n…® uŇčuun maŇčŇčam…®usua, aŇčm mb…®sevisi gumasi a Got…®n…® Utuman gamgaaŇčn iŇčaarir akaar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. \f * \fr 1:1-2 \ft Luk, Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…® mb…®gharan khav os…®ri. A ufhuaragh…®v…®rama os…®risir…® mb…®ghar, a Luk Os…®risira Akamana AghuuŇč.\f*
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Mt 28.17; Mk 16.12; Lu 24.36-49; Ap 10.41; 1 Ko 15.5-7\x* A ufhuaragha mb…®zasi nigha aremigha nomthegha r…®kavisir…® uthusir a thighar Got…®n…® uŇčuun maŇčŇčam…®usua, a nomb…® nigha, a nomb…®usua mb…®sevisi gumasir kh…®va. A bisira avh…®rara men kh…®vasima, mee bar anda ikaaŇči, a nomthegha r…®kavhigha iti. 40 p…®lan uthusi, uthughun khav…®n avhen…® uthusira avh…®rara a nomb…®n men kh…®vagha Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughun gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Lu 24.49; Jo 14.16-17; Ap 2.33\x* Uthughun mav…®n a men phorugha ikha, aphava mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man aghavagharan khav…®n meŇčga an…®…®Ňči, ‚ÄúGee Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®va thaegh maŇčŇča thagh…®ri. Bighana aghuuŇč nan Inaghaves geera an…®…®Ňčm…®usua akama r…®k…®risi thav, a zaami. Gee anaŇčmba oraghi, kha aŇčn gun gem mb…®kemi. Gee aŇčm…®usua gan ikh…®…®.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Mt 3.11; Mk 1.8; Lu 3.16; Jo 1.33; Ap 11.16\x* Jon gumasi rako amisi r…®m…®n mee uruesima, kh…®…® g…®n Got…®n…® Utuman gamgaaŇčn gee uruami.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ais 1.26; Dan 7.17; Amo 9.11; Mt 24.3; Lu 24.21\x* Uthughun mav…®n, mee nori akuvasir…® uthughun, mee aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúIkh…®v, n…®…® uthughun khav…® ativamir gumagh Israeli raniiŇčtima, a nomthegh Israelir…® unuagh…®nan ganaŇčgami, o?‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 1:6 \ft Fhom…®ra Israelir gumasir marsi nori norigha ativasir gumagh ikha non…® unuagh…®nan gari. Iesus…®n…® uthughun, Israeli RomiiŇčn apheeŇčn iti. Iesus…®n…® uthughun khav…®n otogha aruima, gumasira avh…®rara kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si, a RomiiŇčn gavman…® mbatuegh…®va nomb…® Israelir ganaŇčgami. G…®n IsraeliiŇč, unuagh…®nan igharis tharsi andar gan…®va andar apheeŇčn ikaami thughat…®s phat…®.\f*
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mt 24.36; Mk 13.32; 1 Te 5.1\x* Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúBisi otuvamir…® uthugh, nani Inaghaves nomb…®ra non…® uthugh ath…®. Gee theegh…®nam…®usua ana ath…®sir…® uthughun khav ikaaŇčm…®usua. Khara gen bighaaŇč phat…®.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Mt 28.19; Mk 16.15; Lu 24.47-48; Jo 15.27; Ap 2.32; 3.15; 5.32\x* Gumughun Got…®n…® Utum geni iph…®n zighir…®ghtima, gee aŇčn gamgaaŇč nigh…®va, gee Jerusalem…®n nana akam…® ukun…®va Judian distrigh ko, Samarian distrigh…®n maŇč…® unuagh…®nan khav…®n as…®sive bar, men niaghaami.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Iesus Got…®n…® uŇčuun zui
\r (Mak 16.19-20 koma Luk 24.50-53)
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Mk 16.19; Lu 24.50-51; Jo 6.62; 20.17\x* Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®kemigha g…®vagha, aŇčm mb…®sevisi gumasi garav…®re itima Got ana sigharafasima a Got…®n…® uŇčuun guavanandi. Mauthughura mee garav…®re itima guan mav ana mondu.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Mt 28.3; Mk 16.5; Lu 24.4; Jo 20.12; Ap 10.3; 10.30\x* A guavanandima mee khogho ovheen garav…®re itima, gumaghaniiŇč shaaran…® ughuraniiŇč arughava uzuam…®ra men phorugha utu.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mt 24.30; 26.64; Lu 21.27; Jo 14.3; 1 Te 1.10; 4.16; KTH 1.7\x* AniiŇč kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGalilin distrigh…®n gumasi, gee thoghousua khagh…® utuivighav ikha iph…®no ovheen gari? Gumaghan khav Iesus, Got ana nisima a gee thaegha non…® uŇčuun gu. Gee aŇčn ganisima a Got…®n…® uŇčuun gusi mogh…®n, a kamagh…®ra nomthegh zaami.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mee Judas…®n aŇčan niam…®usua Matiasa mb…®sevi
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Lu 24.50\x* Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi Oliv…®n oragha thaegha nomthegha Jerusalem…®n zui. Oliv…®n oragh…®n khav Jerusalem…®n aghangera ikava aŇčn…® uruar kilomitan uvhuav…®ran m…®n gu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Mt 10.2-4; Mk 3.16-19; Lu 6.14-16\x* Mee gua Jerusalem…®n avhen gugha gua mee ma iti r…®phenan avhen iph…®n guavanaaŇči. Meni iz…®…®ri khara, Pita, Jon, Jems ri Andru, Filip ri Tomas, Bartolomiu, Metiu ri Jems, a Alfius…®n otar, Saimon, a SelotiiŇčn phogh…®n gumaghan mav, koma Judas, a Jems…®n otar.
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mt 13.55; Lu 23.49; 23.55; 24.10; Jo 6.42; 7.5\x* Mee m…®ghas…®gha navan uvhuav…®ra ikha nori nigha Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, amisir marsi rako Maria, Iesus…®ni inaghamuuŇč, koma aŇčn…® undoosi ivh…®ra.
\p 
\v 15 Uthusir kharsir avhen gumasi rako amisi Krais…®n phorus tharsi Pita mena ar…®ghan…® utugha akam…® ukuri, men avh…®ra r…®mbombon 120.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Sng 41.9\x* A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNana avheeŇčmbuagha, Got…®n…® Utum fhom…®ra Devit…® amuisi, aŇčna akaman mav…®m mb…®kemi. Akaman khav Got…®m mb…®gharan avheni iti. Akaman khav a Judas…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Kha gumagh Judas, a utuav…®n aphanir gumasir k…®rasima mee Iesus aŇčn…® usuirasi tharsi. Akaman khav thighira otogha g…®va, Devit mb…®kemisi mogh…®ra.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 10.4; Lu 6.16; Ap 1.25\x* Judas fhom…®ra en gumaghan mav, a ivh…®ra ee kha amuir iŇčaara amui.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mt 26.15; 2 Pi 2.15\xt Mt 27.3-8\x* A non oth…®vhan maghat…®ghan uvhues nighava unuagh…®nan mav…® uvhuesi. A unuagh…®nan khav…®n nomb…® ukunigha irima aŇčm mb…®kar…®gh r…®ghoraghirima, aŇčn…® umuu baro oŇčeeghir…®.
\v 19 Kamagh amuisima, Jerusalem…®ni iti tharsi barbar bighan khav…® oraghi, mee unuagh…®nan khav non akaman iz…®…®n khav…®n aŇčga ath…®, Akeldama. AŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh…®n, Ňčaanan…® unuagh…®n.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Sng 69.25; 109.8\x* Pita mb…®Ňčg…® gua kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGot…®m mb…®gharan avheni iti mb…®tisir os…®…®ran khav iti, ‚ÄėAŇčn aŇčan phure ikh…®…®ri, thav ana aŇčanan khav nia thagh…®ri.‚Äô A ivh…®ra kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėA gumaghan aphanan m…®n iŇčaari, gumughun igharisi thav ana amuisir iŇčaar niaŇčga.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 Kamagha amuisima, a m…®ghas…®gha en phorugha ikava eni Ikh…®v Iesus…®n g…®n aruisi gumasi ee thavam mb…®sevighemi.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Mt 3.16; Mk 1.9; 16.19; Lu 3.21; 24.51; Jo 15.27; Ap 4.33\x* Jon gumasi uruesir…® uthugh, ko Iesus…® ufhuaragha r…®k…®nar…®karaghava amusiri iŇčarir…® uthughun ikhegha, zaav…®kava Got Iesus nisi a ee thaegha guavanambosir…® uthughun…® utu. Uthusir kharsir bar en phorugha ikesir gumagha thav ana mb…®sevighemi. Iesus r…®kavhigha g…®vasima kha gumagh aŇčn gani, a en phorugh mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man khav…®n akam…® ukunaŇčga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Mauthughura men gumaghan phuninin iz…®…®ni r…®mboru, Josev, aŇčni iz…®…®n mav Barsabas (aŇčni igharisir iz…®…®n mav Jastus) koma Matias.
\v 24-25 \x - \xo 1:24-25 \xt 1 Sml 16.7; Jer 11.20; Jo 2.25; KTH 2.23\x* Mauthughura mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúIkh…®v, n…®…® gumasir navir averi bar anda ikaaŇči. N…®…® en kh…®va, n…®…® aniiŇčna thavam mb…®sevightima, a Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumagh Judas…®n aŇčan nigh…®va kha iŇčaara ramuaŇčga. IŇčaaran khav Judas ana athaegha aremigha khuur…® uŇčuun gu.‚ÄĚ
\v 26 Mauthughura mee ak…®man aniiŇčni iz…®…®ni os…®righa thooŇčga ath…®gha aniiŇč ivhasvhasima Matias…®ni iz…®…® itir ak…®m iph…®n ikhegha ufhuaraghav…®ra ak…®rei ir…®. Kamagha amuisima mee Matias nigha, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir 11 p…®lan phorugha ana ath…®.
\c 2
\s1 Got…®n…® Utum zeghiri
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Lo 16.9-11; Ap 1.14\x* Pentikos…®n…® uthughun ikh…®vo otosima, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi mee noria akuvagha r…®phenan mav…®n iti. \f * \fr 2:1 \ft Pentikos…®n…® uthughun ikh…®v, aŇčni iz…®…®n mav khara, ombariria r…®ghorir uthughun ikh…®v.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Ap 4.31\x* Mauthughura uzuam…®ra mee orasima n…®n…®…®Ňčn ikh…®van mav Got…®n…® uŇčuun ikhegha zeghira, gamiiŇčn gamgaaŇč m…®n zii. A mee apiighav iti r…®phen bar ana iz…®vagha ana noghi.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Mt 3.11\x* Mee garima bighan mav arivam mb…®zan m…®n otogha b…®ghira uvhuaghuvhuagha men aphanir is…®righa aphighi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mk 16.17; Ap 1.5; 4.31; 10.44-46; 1 Ko 12.10; 13.1\x* Mauthughura Got…®n…® Utum barbar mee iz…®vaghava, gamgaaŇčn meŇčga aniiŇčga meŇčga amuima, mee uŇčuimbar igharisi tharsir akaa v…®Ňčgeeghi.
\p 
\v 5 Uthughun khav…®n Judarir akogh…®n gumasi rako amisi fhom…®ra gua igharisi uŇčuimbar…® unuasir iti tharsi mena marsi nomthegha zaava Jerusalem…®ni iti, mee ivh…®ra Got…®n apheeŇčn iti.
\v 6 Ara mee n…®Ňčn…®…®Ňčn khav…® oraegha zaa bar nori akuvaghav ikava, mee uvhuaghuvhagha orasima gumasi rako amisi men…® uŇčuimbar akaa v…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Ap 1.11\x* Kamagha amuisi mee osemigha atam n…®gh…®n…®si. Ara mee r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuighava azaaghi, ‚ÄúKha mb…®Ňčgeer gumasi mee bar Galilin distrigh…®n gumasira!
\v 8 Manmagh amuigha ee bar…® uvhuaghuvhagha memba orasima mee en…® uŇčuimbar akaara v…®Ňčgeeghi?
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x* Ena marsi, Partian…® unuagh…®n ko Midian…® unuagh…®n ko Elam…®n…® unuagh…®nan ze. Marsi Mesopotemian…® unuagh…®nan zesi gumasi. Marsi Judian distrigh ko Kapadosian distrigh ko Pontus…®n distrigh koma Esian distrigh…®n ze.
\v 10 Marsi Frigian distrigh ko Pamfilian distrigh…®n ze. Marsi Isiv…®n…® unuagh…®n, ko Libian distrigh…®na avheni itira aŇčan, a uŇčuun ik…®van mav Sairinin aghangere iti tharsi mee ze. Marsi Judarir akogh…®n gumasi RomiiŇčn…® uŇčuuni ikhegha zesi tharsi.
\v 11 Ee barbar, Judarir akogh…®n gumasi rako igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi, mee Judariro othevir g…®n zui tharsi, mee ivh…®ra, ena marsi. Ena marsi Krit…®n m…®ghs…®m koma Arebian distrigh…®n gumasi, ee uvhuaghuvhuagha memba orasima mee en…® uŇčuimbar akaar Gota amuisi bisir ikiir gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi!‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Judarir akogh…®n gumasi r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuighava phurama atamatam n…®gh…®n…®ghava norir azaaghi, ‚ÄúKhara theghanan bighaaŇč?‚ÄĚ
\v 13 Judarir akogh…®n gumasir marsi r…®mbovira akaa v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúMee uainir r…®phar avh…®rara amegha oŇčani.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pita akam…® ukuri
\p 
\v 14 Pita, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir 11 p…®lan gumasir phorugha utughav ikha, a gumasi rako amisi mb…®gh…®rav…®ra kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee Judarir akogh…®n gumasi rako Jerusalem…®ni itir gumasi rako amisi, gee bar inderagh…®v…®ra nambaragh. Kh…®…® kha othuivisi bisir gun gem mb…®kemightima, gee anda ikeeŇčgemi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Te 5.7\x* Gumasir kharsi uainiro ov…®siri imboori r…®pha aphava oŇčanisi phat…®. Gee ikaaŇči, khara 9 oklogh…® r…®maaŇčra. \f * \fr 2:15 \ft Judarira akogh…®n gumasi uthughun khav…®n r…®maaŇčra r…®phara oŇčani aphi phat…®. Kamagha amuisi Pita akaman khav…®n mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.\f*
\v 16 Bighan khav oto, khara Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumagh, Joel fhom…®ra mb…®kemisi mogh…®n,
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jol 2.28-32; Sek 12.10; Jo 7.38; Ap 10.45; 21.9\x* ‚ÄėGot kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúG…®n zaamir…® uthusi tharsir kh…®…® non…® Utuman gumasi rako amisi bar mee ran…®…®Ňčgami. Uthughun khav…®n gen otari rako guivi Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumasir m…®n mb…®k…®mtima, gen gumasir iŇčgaa irimbar m…®n bisir gantima, gen gumasir guri iriiŇčmbara akuuva bisir ganaŇčgami.
\v 18 Uthughun khav…®n nan iŇčaarir gumasi rako amisi, kh…®…® non…® utuman ivh…®ra mee raniiŇčtima, mee Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumasir m…®n akaa v…®k…®maŇčga.
\v 19 Gumughun kh…®…® iph…®no ovheen r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuir othevia kh…®v…®va, unuagh…®nan gamgaaŇčn bisira amuaŇčga. Uthughun khav…®n Ňčaan ko ariv koma mb…®turan ikh…®v otuivami.
\v 20 Uthughun khav…®n aro g…®ng…®nightima, ik…®ni Ňčaanan m…®n otuivami. Bisir kharsi ufhuaragh…®v…®ra othuivightima, g…®n Ikh…®v zaamir…® uthugh otuivami. Kha uthughun Ikh…®v non gamgaaŇč ko aŇčaran phorugh zaami.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Ro 10.13\x* Uthughun khav…®n Ikh…®vani iz…®…®n dee tharsi, a men akuruvaghtima mee mb…®gh…®v…®gh…®ighemi.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô
\p 
