\v 30 \x - \xo 2:30 \xt 2 Sml 7.12-13; Sng 89.3-4; 132.11\x* Devit a Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumaghan mav, a ikaaŇči, Got akaman r…®Ňčg…®ran aghavagharan aŇčga aniiŇčga kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėN…®…® ativasir gumagh, kh…®…® n…®…®n aŇčan niam…®usua n…®…®na avava thavam mb…®sevighemi.‚Äô
\v 31 \x - \xo 2:31 \xt Sng 16.10; Ap 13.35\x* Got g…®n ramuaŇčgamir bigh, Devit ana ikaaŇči, a Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh ana aremigh nom r…®kavamir bighaaŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A kamagh…®usue, Got ana thaeghtima aŇčna ar…®ghiresi tharsir ar…®ghan…® umogh…®n avhen ikeghem phat…®. AŇčm mb…®kar…®gh kurighem phat…®ghami. \f * \fr 2:31 \ft GrighiiŇčna akam mee kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúKrais‚ÄĚ, aŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh…®n, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh.\f*
