\v 42 \x - \xo 2:42 \xt Ap 20.7\x* Krais…®na andarsi mee Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi v…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®v oraegha, bisir norira akuruvagha, nori nigha aphava, Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mam…®usua bar vhusvhusi. \f * \fr 2:42 \ft IkeeŇčsi gumasira avh…®rara kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si, ufhuaragha zui Krais…®na andarsi nori akuvagha norir phorughava aphi. Mee amegha g…®vagha, mee Iesus…®n neer…®nofh…®gh ko ŇčaanaŇčgi n…®gh…®n…®gha uvhu…®sir…® uthuu rako uainiro ov…®siri imbooriria aphi.\f*
