\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Sng 55.17; Ap 2.46; 10.3; 10.9; 10.30\x* Uthughun mav…®n aro 3 oklogh…® utu, khara Judarir akogh…®n gumasi Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger uthugh. Uthughun khav…®ra Pita ri Jon Got…® r…®phenan zui.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Jo 9.1; Ap 14.8\x* Uthughun khav…®n navan avhera usu maghat…®si gumaghan mav iti. Gumasi m…®ghas…®gha ana az…®gha gua Got…® r…®phen ighuisi r…®v…®nan it…®man akamanin ana ar…®si. It…®man akamanin khav…®n iz…®…®, It…®man AghuuŇč K…®nara. A khagh ikava aŇčg…®ro ovh…®siv…®usua gumasi rako amisi Got…®n r…®phen ighuisi r…®v…®nana avhen zui tharsi mena azaaghi.
