\v 11 Gumasi rako amisi akaman khav…® oraegha, r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha, akh…®rs…®gha gua gumaghan khav…®n gari. Mee aŇčn garima a Pita ri Jon…®n…® usuiragha, Got…® r…®phenan azuaŇčn…® utughav iti. R…®phenan azuaŇčn khav…®n…® iz…®…®, Solomon…®n AzuaŇč.
\v 12 Uthughun khav…®n Pita kamagh ganigha, mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúIsraeliiŇčn akhogh…®n gumasi rako amisi, thoghousua bighan khav geŇčga amuisima gee r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui? Gee thoghousua mb…®gh…®rav…®ra aŇčn gara kamagh…®usue, aŇčga ti nonira aghavaghari ikama ti, o aŇčga Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn inderaghav…®re ikava, aŇčga kha gumagha amuisima ana arui? Bar phat…®.
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Kis 3.6; 3.15; Mt 22.32; Lu 23.13-25; Ap 2.23; 7.32\x* Ena avhavi Abraham ri Aisak koma Jekov…®n Got, a non iŇčaaran gumagh Iesus bar ana iph…®ufhui. Gee ana aremighaousua ana nigha aphanir gumasir afhar…® ath…®. Pailat ana tham…®raghaousua mb…®ger…® uthughun, gee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėEe thange aŇčn vhusvhusi phat…®!‚Äô Ara gee ak…®ran aŇčga ase.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Mt 27.15-23; Mk 15.6-14; Lu 23.13-23; Jo 19.12-15\x* Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn othevira aghuira amui gumagh, gee aŇčgi iph…®rph…®righava, gumaghan maghat…®gh noriv…®usua ana tham…®raghaousua Pailat…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A gumasi v…®suagh…®usuesi anda ar…®ghiresir gumagh.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Ap 1.8; 2.24; 2.32; 2.36; 4.10\x* GeŇčga amui gee aŇčam…®ra iti gumagh, gee aŇčm mb…®suesi ana aremisi Got aŇčga amuisima a nomthegha r…®kavhi. AŇčga noni bighan khav…®n ganigha ana ikeeŇčgava aŇčn gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Mt 9.22; Ap 4.10; 14.9\x* AŇčga Iesus…®n iz…®…®n n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar iti. Iesus…®n iz…®…®ra, gee ganigha ikeeŇčsi gumaghan khav, a gamgaaŇč nii. AŇčgan n…®gh…®n…®ghan aghavaghar Iesus…®n ikava bighan khuaŇčga amuisima, n…®gh…®n…®ghan aghavagharan khav…®ra kha gumagh amuisima, a bar indera, gee thighira nori aŇčn gari.
