\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Lu 23.34; Jo 16.3; 1 Ko 2.8; 1 Ti 1.13\x* Nana andarsi, kh…®…® kamagh ikaaŇči, gee amuisiro oth…®v gee ana ikeeŇčsi phat…®, gen gumasiri ikii ivh…®ra.
