\v 21 Got bar fhom…®ra fhom…®ra nona ambuuŇčn gumasi v…®kemisima, mee kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėThighira Iesus Got…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®…®, maaŇč…® Got kha bisi ramutima anda nomthegh bisiri iŇčgaar m…®no othuivighemi.‚Äô Got mb…®kemisi mogh…®n, bisi bar othuivhami.
