\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Lo 18.15-19; Ap 7.37\x* Moses fhom…®ra kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėGot gen Ikh…®v, nan m…®n akam nigha zesi gumaghan mav, a gena ar…®ghan gena thavam mb…®sevighemi. Gee, aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeer bisi, gee bar andavaragh…®va anda ramu.
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Wkp 23.29\x* AŇčm mbarasi phat…®si tharsi, Got meŇčga as…®ghasiighemi. Mee nomthegh Got…®n gumasi rako amisir phorugh ikaami thughat…®s phat…®.‚Äô \f * \fr 3:23 \ft Moses mb…®kemisira akam gee ana ikaaŇčm…®usua Lo mb…®gharan 18.15-19 gan. Pita Moses…®na akaman gum…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, Iesus nomb…®ra kha akam nigha ziir gumagh.\f*
