\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt Stt 12.3; 18.18; 22.18; Ro 9.4; 9.8; Ga 3.8; 3.26\x* Got fhom…®ra nona akam nigha zesi gumasi akamana aghavagharan meŇčga aniiŇčsima, gee men boorir m…®n ikh…®va, akaar aghavagharir kharsi ivh…®ra gena andarsi. Got fhom…®ra akama r…®Ňčg…®rana aghavagharan gena avhavir phorugha aŇčga amuisima, gee men boorir m…®n ikh…®…®, akama r…®Ňčg…®ran aghavagharan khav, a ivh…®ra genav. Got kamagh Abraham…®m mb…®kemisi mogh…®n, ‚ÄėN…®…®na avhavir otara thav otoghtima, kh…®…® aŇčm…®usua inderagh…®v…®ra kha unuagh…®nan iti gumasi rako amisi bar mee ramuaŇčga.‚Äô
\v 26 \x - \xo 3:26 \xt Mt 10.5; Lu 24.47; Ap 13.32-33; 13.46\x* Got kamagh vhusvhusi, gee uvhuaghuvhuagh nono othevir maghat…®sia thaeghtima, kamagh…® ramutima a inderagh…®v…®ra gee ramuaŇčga. Bighan khav…®usua a noni iŇčaaran gumagham mb…®sevigha gem…®usua ufhuaragha ana amanda.‚ÄĚ
\c 4
\s1 Pita ri Jon Judarir os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenan iti
