\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Lu 22.4; 22.52\x* Pita ri Jon gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasi rako, Got…® r…®phenan garir gumasir aphan koma, SadiusiiŇčn phogh…®n gumasi marsi, mee zaava aniiŇčm mbato. \f * \fr 4:1 \ft Got…® r…®phenan garir gumasir aphan, a Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumaghan mav. A, Livaina akhogh…®n gumasi meŇčga ativagha men garima, mee Got…® r…®phenan mb…®rogh…®n iŇčaarava bisir garir…® umbueeŇčmba ath…®van gumaghan iŇčaarigha amui.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Mt 22.23; Ap 23.8\x* Ara mee ikaaŇči, Pita ri Jon, Iesusa aremigha nom r…®kavisi bighan khav…®n gun gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčgeeghi. Kamagha amuisima gumasir aphani, men navi aniiŇčm…®usua bar maghat…®ghi.
