\v 6 Anas, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikh…®v,, a ivh…®re itima, Kaiafas ri Jon ko Aleksander koma Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikh…®van andarsir marsi, mee ivh…®re iti.
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 21.23; Ap 7.27\x* Mee mb…®kemisima, gumasi Pita ri Jon nighava mena ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn zesi, mee magh…®ra aniiŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo aghavagharan manav nigha, th…®…®Ňčn iz…®…®n aŇčgo kha bisigha amui?‚ÄĚ
