\v 9 Gee ti aŇčga akurasir gumaghan…® usuan maghat…®ghan khav…®usua aŇčgana azaaŇčs…®ghaousua, gee ti ivh…®ra ikaaŇčm…®usua, gumaghan khav a manmagh…®re indera.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Ap 2.24; 3.6; 3.13-16\x* Mamagh…®n gee bar ivh…®re ikaaŇčtima Israel…®n iti tharsi mee ivh…®ra bar ikeeŇčg…®ri. Khara NasaretiiŇčn gumagh Krais Iesus…®n iz…®…®n gen ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn…® utughavi iti gumagh, a nomthegha indera. Gumaghan khav Iesus, gee ana nigha khani ighuuvan aŇčga afhusi, ana aremisi Got aŇčga amuisima a nomthegha r…®kavhi.
