\v 13 Mee Pita ri Jon…®n garima aniiŇč bar aghavagharighava avhighavisi phat…®ghava mem mb…®Ňčgeema, mee aniiŇčn ganighava ikaaŇči, aniiŇč surea amuisi phat…®. AniiŇč phura gumaghan kh…®nani. Mee aniiŇčn gara r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha kamagh…®usue, gumaghan khaniiŇč Iesus…®n phorughava arui.
\v 14 Mee gumaghan khav…®n gari, a ufhuaragha usu maghat…®ghi, thighira, a Jon ri Pitan phorugha utughav itima, mee bigha thav…®m mb…®k…®man iŇčgura.
