\v 19-20 \x - \xo 4:19-20 \xt Ap 5.29\xt Ap 1.8; 22.15; 1 Jo 1.1-3\x* Mee aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgema Pita ri Jon men akam…® ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčga noniiŇč ganighava oraesi bisi aŇčga andar guaŇčsighem thughat…®s phat…®, aŇčga andar gun…®m mb…®k…®m…®v…®re ikaami. Gee nori n…®gh…®n…®gh, oth…®vhan manav Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn indera, aŇčga Got…®n akamam mbaraghami, o aŇčga gen akamam mbaraghami?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21-22 Pita ri Jon Got…®n gamgaaŇčn amuisi gumagh inderaghava, a 40 p…®lan ombarigha afhira. Kamagha amuisi gumasi rako amisi nori bisir kharsir gari anda othuivisima, mee Got…®ni iz…®…® ufhii. Kamagha amuisima, gumasira aphani uvhuesan maghat…®ghan aniiŇč ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua phura n…®gh…®n…®si, mee manmagh…®ra aniiŇč ramuti. Mee aniiŇčm mb…®soghousua amuava mee gumasi rako amisir avhighavhisi mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r aghavagharir marsi aniiŇčga amuighava aniiŇč amandasima aniiŇč zui.
\s1 N…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti tharsi Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi
\p 
\v 23 Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenan avhen itir gumasi Pita ri Jona thaesima aniiŇč azenaŇčgi ir…®gha nomthegha nona andarsiv…®usua gu. AniiŇč Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikii rako igharisi gumasira aphani aniiŇčn mb…®kemisir akaar gun nona andarsi bar mem mb…®kemi.
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt Kis 20.11; Neh 9.6; Sng 146.6\x* Mee kamagh oraeghava nori akuvaghava Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Mee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEn Ikh…®v en gari thav, n…®…® ovhee ko unuagh…®naŇčga amuighava, oŇčar ivh…®ra amuighava andar iti bisi ivh…®ra bar andagha amui.
