\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Mt 27.1-2; Mk 15.1; Lu 23.1; 23.7-11; Jo 18.28-29; Ap 3.13\x* Bar guisimbaaŇčra, Herot ri Pontius Pailat koma Israelir gumasi, rako igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi ivh…®ra, mee Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuun nori akuvaghava othevir maghat…®sir Got…®n iŇčaaran gumaghan aghuuŇč, Iesus ramuam…®usuava akaa v…®sosi. A n…®…® fhom…®ra non iŇčariv…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh.
\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt Ap 2.23; 3.18\x* Mee n…®…®n gamgaaŇč ko n…®…®n n…®gh…®n…®ghan g…®n zui, n…®…® fhom…®ra otogha mb…®kemisir bisi.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Ap 9.27; 13.46; 19.8; Ef 6.19\x* Ikh…®v, mee avhighevisir akaar eŇčga aniiŇčsi, n…®…® akaar kharsighi n…®gh…®n…®gh. Ena akuraghtima ee uthugh aghavagharigh…®va avhighevhighem phat…®gh…®va n…®…®na akam…® ukunaŇčgami.
\v 30 N…®…® nona afharimuun ar…®mar…®r gumasir ar…®ghtima mee inderaghami. N…®…® gamgaaŇčn bisira avh…®rara ko r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuir othevi ramutima anda Iesus…®n iz…®…®no othuivhami, a n…®…®n iŇčaaran gumaghan aghuuŇč.‚ÄĚ
