\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Ap 2.4; 4.29; 16.26\x* Mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®kemigha g…®vasima, mee itir aŇčan anughava amandaghava, aŇčn…® Utum meŇčgi iz…®vasima, mee avhighavisi phat…®gha Got…®na akam…® ukuri.
