\v 32 \x - \xo 4:32 \xt Ap 2.44-45; 2 Ko 13.11; 1 Pi 3.8\x* Uthughun khav…®n n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti tharsi, mee bar navan…® uvhuav…®ra ko n…®gh…®n…®ghan…® uvhuav…®re iti. Men thav nomb…®ra bigha thav…® nomb…®na amendasi phat…®, mee nori nighav…®ra bisi barbar andar gari.
