\v 36 \x - \xo 4:36 \xt Ap 11.22-26; 13.2-3\x* Gumaghan mav Josev, a Livaina akhogh…®n gumagh. Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi mee Barnabas…®na aŇčga ar…®si. AŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh gu, gumasira akuruvagha gamgaaŇč meŇčga an…®ndir gumagh. Barnabas Saiprus…®n m…®ghs…®man…® uŇčuun ze.
