\c 5
\s1 Ananaias ri Safaira Got…®n khoru amui
\p 
\v 1 Gumaghan mav Ananaias, aŇčna amuuŇč Safaira, aniiŇč ivh…®ra non unuagh…®nan mav amandagha aŇčn…® uvhues nii.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Ap 4.34-37\x* Mauthughura aniiŇč ivh…®re ikaaŇči, Ananaias aŇčg…®r ov…®sir marsi nomb…®usua andar…® usuira. Ano ofh…®ghan muaŇč nigha Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir khorigha amua meŇčga an…®…®Ňči.
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Lo 23.21; Lu 22.3; Jo 13.2\x* A meŇčga aniiŇčsima, Pita kamagh Ananaias…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® theghousuava, satana thaesima a n…®…®n navan avhee iz…®vasima, n…®…® Got…®n…® Utuman khorigha amui? N…®…® theghousua unuagh…®nan…® uvhuesana aŇčg…®r ovh…®sir marsi n…®…® nomb…®usua andar…® usuira?
\v 4 Khara n…®…®n…® unuagh…®na, n…®…® nomb…® vhusvhusigha ana amanda. AŇčn…® uvhuesan aŇčg…®ro ovh…®si ivh…®ra n…®…®n aŇčg…®r ovh…®sir…®. N…®…® manmagh…®ra n…®gh…®n…®gha nona aŇčg…®ro ov…®sir kharsir en khorigha amui? N…®…® gumasir khoru amuir phat…®, n…®…® Got…®n khoru amui.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Ananaias kamagh oraegha ir…®ghava aremi. Magh…®ra gumasi rako amisi bighan khav…® oraegha avhighevisima ikh…®v mee nii.
\v 6 Magh…®ra gumasir iŇčgaa zaava aŇčn khuma anuegha ana nigha ak…®ran gua ana umogh…® ath…®.
\p 
\v 7 Gumughun, aron iŇčeendagh uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav nigha g…®vasima, aŇčna amuuŇč ikeeŇčsi phat…®gha avhen zii.
\v 8 A zima, Pita aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nam mb…®k…®m, khara guisim baaŇčran…® unuagh…®n…® uvhues, n…®…® man ko aŇčgo ana nisi o?‚ÄĚ Am mb…®Ňčgeema a kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúAŇčre, bar aŇčn…® uvhuesara.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Pita kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo manmagh…®usua ivh…®ra vhusvhusigha Got…®n…® Utuman khoru amui? N…®…® gan! N…®…®n manan khum nigha gua umogh…® ath…®si gumasi it…®man akamaniiŇčn iti. Thighira mee ivh…®ra n…®…®n khum nigh ak…®ran maŇčŇčanga.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Pita mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, Safaira aŇčn…® usuaniiŇčn ir…®ghava aremi. Gumasir iŇčgaa avhen zaa garima aŇčna aremisi mee ana nigha ak…®ran gugha aŇčn manan…® umogh…® mb…®rogh…®rama ana ath…®.
\v 11 Mauthughura avhighevhigheni ikh…®v Krais…®na andarsi bar mem mbato. Gumasi, bisir kharsiva oraesi tharsi, mee bar ivh…®ra avhighavighi.
\s1 GamgaaŇčn bisira avh…®rara othuivi
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Ap 2.43; 4.32; 14.3; Ro 15.19; 2 Ko 12.12\x* Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi gamgaaŇčn bisira avh…®rara ko r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuir othevi avh…®rara, gumasi rako amisir thooŇčn andagha amui. N…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti gumasi rako amisi, mee Solomon…®n AzuaŇčn m…®ghas…®gha nori akuvi.
\v 13 Gumasir igharis tharsi, men phoghaousua thange n…®gh…®n…®si phat…®. Mee meni iz…®…®ri ufha ikaaŇči, mee oth…®vhana aghuuŇčga amui.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Ap 2.41; 21.20\x* Marsi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavagharan Ikh…®van ikha mena avhen zuima, men r…®mbomboni bar guavanambo.
