\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Mk 6.56; Ap 19.11-12\x* Uthughun khav…®n ivh…®ra Jerusalem mb…®rogh…®n itir…® uŇčuimbar sovsegher gumasira avh…®rara, mee nona ar…®mar…®r gumasi rako amisi nigha ze. Mauthughura mee ivh…®ra non gumasi rako amisir…® unduur maghat…®si aphasasi tharsi nigha zesima, mee barbar nomthegha indera.
\s1 Ensel Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir akurasi, mee r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha thaghi
