\p Mauthughura Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikh…®v nona akuruvasi tharsir phorugha zaa, Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenana garir gumasir d…®…®sima, mee gua nori akuvagha iti. Israel…®n iz…®…®ri iti gumasira aruura nori akuvagha iti. Mee Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi nigh zaaousua r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan r…®phenan garir gumaghousua akama amanda.
\v 22 Mauthughura ganganir gumasi marsi gua r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha r…®phenan otogha garima mee khagh iti phat…®sima, mee nomthegha zaava bighan khav…®n gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi,
\v 23 ‚ÄúEe r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha r…®phenan garima mee inderaghav…®ra an ith…®…®raakaa r…®kuusima, r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan r…®phenan garir gumasi aŇčn ith…®…®ra akaar utuivighav iti. Magh…®ra ee ith…®…® ukuigha garima, thav avheni iti phat…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
