\nb 
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Ap 7.58; 8.4; 11.19; 22.20\x* Uthughun khav…®n Sol ivh…®re ikha bighan khav…®n ganigha kamagh…®usue, a indera.
\s1 Sol Krais…®n phorus tharsi phuv…®ra mera afharavasi
\p Kha uthughun mee Stiven…®m mb…®suesima ana aremi. Ana aremisima mee Jerusalem…®ni iti Krais…®n phorus tharsi phuv…®ra mee mb…®sogha, othevir maghat…®sir meŇčga amui. Kamagha amuisima, Krais…®n phorus tharsi bar ara Judian distrigh ko Samarian distrigh…®n gue. Uthughun khav…®n Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi Jerusalem…®ni iti.
