\v 13 Mauthughura Saimon ivh…®ra n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar ikava a ivh…®rou urue. Uthughun khav…®n Saimon Filiv…®n g…®a arua garima, Filip r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuir othevi rako gamgaaŇčn bisir ikiigha amuima anda othuivima, a r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui.
