\v 20 \x - \xo 8:20 \xt Mt 10.8; Ap 2.38; 10.45\x* Pita kamagh aŇčm mbeŇčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…®na aŇčg…®r ov…®si n…®…®n phorugh…®v…®ra maghatiighemi. Got a bighan aghuuŇčn m…®n an…®…®ndir bigha thav aŇčg…®r ov…®sir uvhuesi a? Bar phat…®! Bighan khav…®usua n…®…® nona aŇčg…®ro ov…®si phorugh…®v…®ra mbuŇčŇčue phat…®sir arivan maŇčŇčaŇčga.
