\v 27-28 \x - \xo 8:27-28 \xt Ais 56.3-7; Sef 3.10; Jo 12.20\x* Kamagh…®n amuisima, a magh…®ra zui. A utuav…®na ar…®ghan Itiopian…® unuagh…®nan gumaghan mav…®a oto. A gumaghan aphan, a Itiopian…® unuagh…®nan ativasira amighan aŇčg…®r ov…®sir garir gumagh. Amighan iz…®…® Kandasi. Gumaghan khav Jerusalem…®n gugha Got…®ni iz…®…® ufhuegha nomthegha zii. A karis…®a apheragha, Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumagh Aisaian mb…®gharan gari.
\v 29 Mauthughura Got…®n…® Utum Filiv…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® maŇč…®va karis…®n munav…®n aghan ikh…®…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 30 Mauthughura Filip akh…®ghavt…®gha gua karis…®n aghan gugha Itiopian…® unuagh…®nan gumagha orasima, a Aisaia, Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumagham mb…®gharan gari. Kamagha amuisima Filip aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® gari bighan khav n…®…® ana ikeeŇčsi o phat…®?‚ÄĚ
\v 31 \x - \xo 8:31 \xt Jo 16.13\x* Itiopian…® unuagh…®nan gumagh ana ikara, ‚ÄúKh…®…® manmagh…®ra ikaaŇč ti? Thav nan niagh…®tima, kh…®…® ikeeŇčgemi. N…®…® z…®vanaŇč nan phorugh raphera.‚ÄĚ
