\v 32-33 \x - \xo 8:32-33 \xt Ais 53.7-8\x* Itiopian…® unuagh…®nan gumagh Got…®m mb…®gharan itir akaar kharsir gari, ‚ÄúA sivsiv…®n m…®n mee aŇčm mb…®soghousuava, ana nigha gu. Mee sivsiviir…® uŇčusira ar…®sia r…®ph…®rousuava amuima anda in…®m…®re iti. Kamagh…®ra gumaghan khav, mee aŇčm mb…®soghousuava amuima, a phura in…®m…®re ikha bigha thav…®m mb…®Ňčge phat…®. Mee bar aŇčn amevagha, inderaghav…®ra an os…®mnd…®siva oragha anda r…®k…®risi phat…®. Kamagha amuisima, a boorir phat…®, manmagh aŇčn niagh…® ti? Mee an ik…®rana aghuuŇč g…®vasima, a nomthegha unuagh…®nan iti phat…®.‚ÄĚ
