\v 34 Mauthughura …®nan gumagh Filiv…®n azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® na mb…®k…®m. Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumagh, a th…®…®Ňčn gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi? A nomb…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi, o igharis tharsi v…®Ňčgeeghi?‚ÄĚ
