\p 
\v 38 Mauthughura …®nan gumagh karis…®n…® usuisi gumagham mb…®Ňčgema, a karis…® amuisima a utu. Mauthughura Filiv ri …®nan gumagh r…®m…®na avhen gueghir…®si, Filiv ana urue.
