\c 9
\s1 Sol non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®ra
\r (Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi 22.4-16 koma 26.9-18)
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 9:1-2 \xt Ap 8.3; Ga 1.13; 1 Ti 1.13\x* Kha uthughun Sol Iesus…®n suren gumasigha as…®ghas…®gh…®va, mee mb…®soghtima mee ar…®ghiraousua, mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r gamgaegha amuav…®re iti. Kamagha amuisi, a Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikh…®v…®ousua gua kamagha aŇčn azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuun itir gumasira aphaniv…®usua mb…®gharia os…®ri. Gumasi aphani kharsi Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phenir gari. N…®…® osira kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėGumagha thav o amigha thav, Iesus…®n…® utuav…®n g…®n maŇč…®tima, Sol aŇčn ganigh…®va, aŇčn…® usuiragh maŇčŇč…® r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan iti gumaghan m…®n ana ikhegh…®va, Jerusalem…®n ana amandaghami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3 \xt Ap 22.6; 26.12; 1 Ko 15.8\x* Mauthughura a Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuna aghan zima ovheen aŇčaran gamgaaŇč aŇčgi isira.
