\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt Ap 5.39; 1 Ko 15.8\x* Ana aŇčm mb…®kemisima Sol azaaghi, ‚ÄúIkh…®v, n…®…® th…®…®Ňčra?‚ÄĚ Mauthughura a kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKh…®…® Iesus, n…®…® nar afharavasi.
\v 6 N…®…® r…®kavigh…®va, uŇčuun maaŇč…®. Gumughun gumagha thav n…®…®ra amuaŇčgami bisir gun n…®…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga.‚ÄĚ
