\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Ap 22.9; 26.13\x* Uthughun khav…®n gumasi Sol…®n phorugha zui tharsi, mee phura gumaghan mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r k…®niva oraegha gumagha thav…®n ganis phat…®. Kamagha amuisi mee mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…® phat…®gha phure iti.
\v 8 Magh…®ra Sol nomthegha r…®kavhigha, non ar…®maghaniiŇč ukuigha, a bigha thav…®n ganis phat…®. AŇčn phorugha arui gumasi ana agharaniiŇčn usuiragha ana nigha mee Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuun zui.
\v 9 A Damaskus…®ni itima aŇčna ar…®maghaniiŇč uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav…®n maghat…®ghav…®re itima, ana aghaa thav ko r…®m…® thav amesi phat…®.
