\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Ap 8.3\x* Mauthughura Ananaias ana ikara, ‚ÄúIkh…®v, kh…®…® orasima, gumasira avh…®rara gumaghan khav…®n gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, mee kamagh…®usue, a n…®…®n gumasi rako amisi Jerusalem…®na avheni iti tharsi iphasa meŇčga amui.
\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt Ap 9.1-2; 9.21; 22.16; 1 Ko 1.2; 2 Ti 2.22\x* Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikii, akamana aghavagharan aŇčm mb…®nam…®naaŇč ath…®si a ze. Gumasi rako amisi n…®…®n iz…®…®n deer tharsi, a men…® usuighava r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha rath…®ghami.‚ÄĚ
\v 15 \x - \xo 9:15 \xt Ap 25.13; 25.22; 26.17; 27.24; Ro 1.5; 1 Ko 15.10; Ga 2.7-8; 1 Ti 2.7\x* An aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeema Ikh…®v kamagh Ananaias…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® maaŇč…®! Gumaghan khav, mara kh…®…® mb…®sevisir iŇčaaran gumagh. A nan iz…®…®n gun igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi rako meŇčga ativasi tharsi ko Israelir gumasiv…®usua maŇčaŇčga.
\v 16 \x - \xo 9:16 \xt Ap 20.23; 21.11; 2 Ko 11.23-28\x* Gumughun a nani iz…®…®n os…®mnd…®si rako mb…®zasi niaŇčgamir tharsi, kh…®…® andar aŇčn kh…®vaghami.‚ÄĚ
