\v 17 \x - \xo 9:17 \xt Ap 13.52; 22.12-13\x* Mauthughura Ananaias r…®phenan gua ana avhen gu. A nona afharimuun Sol…®ni iph…®n ath…®gha, kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúNana avheeŇčphom, Sol, n…®…® khagh zima Ikh…®v Iesus…® utuav…®n n…®…® mbato. N…®…® nomthegh ganti, Got…®n…® Utum n…®…® iz…®vaghaousua, kamagha amuisima a na amandasi kh…®…® ze.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Magh…®ra bar uzuam…®ra, osiran inagh…®nan m…®n garir bigh…®n Sol…®na ar…®maghaniiŇčn ikeghava ukuighir…®. Kamagh…®n amuisi a thighira nomthegha gari. A magh…®ra r…®kavhisima mee Iesus…®ni iz…®…®n ana urue.
\v 19 Mauthughura ana aghaer marsi amegha g…®n nomthegha non gamgaaŇč nii. Kamagha amuigha Sol Iesus…®n suren gumasir phorugha uthusi marsir Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuni ikhee.
\s1 Sol akamana aghuuŇčn Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuna ana ukuri
