\v 20 Sol Iesus…®n suren gumasir phorugha Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuni ikha magh…®ra Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phenir akam…® ukura kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúIesus a Got…®n Otar.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 \x - \xo 9:21 \xt Ap 8.3; Ga 1.13; 1.23\x* Sol…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, mee aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®v oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuighava norira azaaghi, ‚ÄúKhara ti gumaghan khav…®ra, a Jerusalem…®ni ikha Iesus…®n iz…®…®n deer gumasi rako amisi, a men…® usuigha mee rafharavasi? A ti mee nigh maaŇč…® r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan iti gumasir m…®n mee ikhegh…®va Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikiir afharir rar…®ghaousua, mamagh amuigha a khagh ze?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Ap 17.3; 18.5; 18.28\x* Mauthughura Sol…®na akam bar gamgaeŇčga guavanambosi a inderaghav…®ra mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…® v…®n…®Ňčgaria b…®gha Iesus a Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh ana akam…® ukuri. Damaskus…®ni iti Judarir akogh…®n gumasi r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuighava mb…®k…®man iŇčgura.
\s1 Judarii Sol…® mb…®soghosuava amuima ana ara gu
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt Ap 23.12; 25.3; 2 Ko 11.23\xt 2 Ko 11.32-33\x* Uthusira avh…®rara guesima, Judarii Sol mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousuava utuaviv…®usua urui.
\v 24 Mee aŇčm mb…®soghousuava arue rako r…®maŇčgarir m…®ghas…®gha aŇčm…®usua uŇčuun r…®v…®nan ith…®…®r akaar garima, mee aŇčm mb…®kemisima Sol men n…®gh…®n…®ghan maghat…®ghan khav ikaaŇči.
\v 25 Mauthughura aŇčn g…®na aruir gumasi, mee r…®maaŇčn aŇčm mb…®kemisi ana akh…®raman ikh…®v aŇčga apherasima, mee gamiiŇč nii r…®v…®nan thooŇčn mav…®n ana thaesima a gueghira uŇčuun r…®v…®nan ak…®ran ir…®.
