\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 9:26 \xt Ap 22.17; Ga 1.17-19\x* Sol Jerusalem…®n zegha, Iesus…®n suren gumasi phorugh ikhaousua amuima mee n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar kamagh aŇčni iti phat…®, a Iesus…®n suren gumagh. Kamagha amuigha mee bar Sol…®na avhighavighi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 9:27 \xt Ap 4.36; 9.4; 9.20-22; 1 Ko 9.1; 15.8\x* Ara Barnabasa ana nigha aŇčn gun Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi v…®k…®mam…®usua zui. A mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúSol…® utuav…®n gua Ikh…®van gani. Mauthughura Ikh…®v aŇčm mb…®kemisima a DamaskusiiŇčn thav…®na avhighaviisi phat…®gha, Iesus…®ni iz…®…®n akam…® ukuri.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Sol Jerusalem…®n inderaghav…®ra men phorugha aruava men phorugha ikava avhighavisi phat…®gha Iesus…®ni iz…®…®n akam…® ukura guav…®re iti.
\v 29 \x - \xo 9:29 \xt Ap 6.1; 9.23; 11.20; 2 Ko 11.26\x* A Judari GrighiiŇčna akama mb…®Ňčger gumasir phorugha mee nori v…®Ňčg…® nori vatosi, kamagha amuisima mee aŇčm mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousuava amui.
\v 30 \x - \xo 9:30 \xt Ga 1.21\x* Mauthughura Krais…®n phorusi tharsi kamagh oraegha ikeeŇčga, ana nigha Sisarian…® uŇčuun gueghir…®gha ana nigha Tarsus…®n…® uŇčuun ana amanda. \f * \fr 9:30 \ft G…®n Barnabas Sol nigh Antiogh…®n maŇčŇčam…®usua, gua Tarsus…®n…® uŇčuun aŇčm…®usua uri. N…®…® Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaari 11.25…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 31 Judian distrigh ko Galilin distrigh ko Samarian distrigh…®n avhen iti Krais…®n…® andarsi, uthughun khav…®n navana am…®…®Ňčnd…®ghan ikha inderaghav…®ra itima, Got…®n…® Utum gamgaaŇč meŇčga an…®ndi. Kamagha amuisima Krais…®na andarsi r…®mbomboni guavanandi. Gumasi rako amisi Got…®n avhighavighava aŇčna apheeŇčn iti.
\s1 Pita Ainias…® amuisima a nomthegha indera
\p 
\v 32 Uthughun khav…®n Pita uŇčuimba bar andagha aruigha, Lidan…® uŇčuun itir Got…®n gumasi rako amisir ganam…®usua zui.
\v 33 A gua uŇčuun khav…®n gumaghan mav…® oto, aŇčni iz…®…® Ainias. AŇčn…® usue rako afhari am…®rasima, a 8 p…®lan ombaarir akhogh…®re ikhee.
\v 34 \x - \xo 9:34 \xt Ap 3.6; 3.16; 4.10\x* Uthughun khav…®n Pita kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAinias, Krais Iesus n…®…®Ňčga amuisi, n…®…® indera. N…®…® r…®kavigh…®va nona akogha r…®k…®r.‚ÄĚ Magh…®ra Ainias…® uzuam…®ra r…®kavi.
\v 35 \x - \xo 9:35 \xt 1 Sto 5.16; Ap 11.21\x* A r…®kavima Lidan…® uŇčuu ko Saron…®n mb…®naaŇčn iti gumasi rako amisi, mee aŇčn ganigha non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®ragha n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Ikh…®van iti.
