\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Kis 12.1-27\x* A Pitan…® usuiraghava ana nigha r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha ath…®. Ana nigha mb…®zorusir gumasir 4 p…®la ikh…®sir phosir afhar…® ath…®. Mee uthusi uvhuaghuvhuagha aŇčn gari. 4 p…®lan gumasir phosir kharsi, mee anda uvhuaghuvhuagha 4 p…®la gumasi nisima mee aŇčn gari. Herot, Israeli Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthughun ishaman ikh…®van khav g…®vaghtima, a Pita nigh gumasi rako amisira avh…®rira ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenan rar…®ghaousua.
