\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt Ap 5.23\x* Uthughun khav…®n Herot Pita nigh…®va os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenam…®usua maŇčŇčam…®usua uthughun mav…® ath…®. R…®maaŇčn khav…®n, am…®n thighar itima, mee ukuaghavan phuninin ana ikhesima am mb…®zorughan gumaghan phuniiŇčnina ar…®ghana akui. Mauthughura igharisi mb…®zorsir gumasir marsi r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha r…®phenan aŇčm…®usua gara it…®mana akamaniiŇčn iti.
\v 7 Uzuam…®ra Ikh…®van enselo otosima, aŇčn aŇčaar r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha r…®phenana avhen is…®ra. Ensel Pitani ivher…®m mb…®suegha aŇčga aghuragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® uzuam…®ra r…®kavi!‚ÄĚ Magh…®ra aŇčna agharaniiŇč ikesi ukuakuaghavaniiŇč fh…®righir…®gha unuagh…®naŇčgi ir…®.
\v 8 Mauthughura ensel aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúShaara sharagh…®va aŇčgarir shaaria shara.‚ÄĚ An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Pita kamagha amuigha g…®vasima ensel aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® non shaaran…® uruara thava sharagh nan g…®n z…®…®.‚ÄĚ
