\v 17 \x - \xo 12:17 \xt Ap 13.16; 19.33; 21.40\x* Mauthughura Pita nona afharaniiŇčn mee r…®khaghar…®sima, mee n…®m…®re iti. Mauthughura aŇčn Ikh…®v Judarii r…®phenan k…®rt…®ghana avhen ana nigha ak…®ra ath…®sir othevir gun men niazi. A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee bisir kharsir gun Jems nona afhoghumasir phorugha ivh…®ra mem mb…®k…®m…®ri.‚ÄĚ Gumughun Pita mee thaegha igharisira aŇčanan gu. \f * \fr 12:17 \ft Jems…®n khav a Iesus…®n…® undoogh. N…®…® Galesian 1.19…®n gan. Jems Jerusalem…®ni itir Krais…®na andarsi gumaghana aphanan oto.\f*
