\v 18 \x - \xo 12:18 \xt Ap 5.22-24\x* Am…®n itirasima, mb…®zorsir gumasi Pitaousua garava avheeŇči. Mee bar r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha norira, norira azaaŇčs…®gha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúPita manav…®n gu?‚ÄĚ
