\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt 1 Kin 5.9-11; Ese 27.17\x*Mee noriv…®usua nira aghae bisi anda Herot ativagha garir…® uŇčuun iti. Herota avhesan ik…®van Tair ri Saidon…®n gumasi rako amisir itima, mee kha bighaaŇčm…®usua thighira nori akuvagha aŇčn ganam…®usua zui. Mee ufhuaraghav…®ra Blastus…®m mb…®kemisi a men phorugha navan am…®…®Ňčnd…®gh nigha g…®va. Blastus, ana ativasir gumagh Herot akuira aŇčanan garir gumagh. G…®n Herot men…® ukuarukuvighava andaran khava g…®vaousua mb…®kemisima, mee aŇčn ganam…®usua zui.
