\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Ap 11.27\x* Antiogh…®ni iti Krais…®n…® andarsi mena marsi iti, Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumasi rako fh…®gh…®n gumasi. Meni iz…®…®ri Barnabas, ri Simeon (aŇčni iz…®…®n mav Niger), Sairinin…® uŇčuun gumagh Lusius, ri Manain (ana ativasir gumagh Herot…®n r…®kurukum, a Herot…®n phorugha aghuuŇči) koma Sol. \f * \fr 13:1 \ft Iz…®…®n khav Niger, aŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh gu uph…®gh. Gumasir marsi kamagh…®usue, Simeon Niger, ana Afrikan gumagh.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Ap 9.15; Ro 10.15; Ga 1.15; Ef 3.7-8; 1 Ti 2.7; Hi 5.4\x* Uthughun mav…®n Krais…®na andarsi, mee Got…®n apheeŇčn ikava nori nigha Got…® aniiŇčgava, Got…®n phorugh…® mb…®k…®mam…®usuava aghae thaghi. Uthughun khav…®n Got…®n…® Utum kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKh…®…® Barnabas ri Sol noni iŇčariv…®usua aniiŇčn d…®…®gha. Gee iŇčaaran khav…®usua aniiŇč amb…®sevightima, aniiŇč nan iŇčaaraousua maaŇč…®.‚ÄĚ
