\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt Ap 15.39\x* Got…®n…® Utum Barnabas ri Sol amandasima, aniiŇč Selusian…® uŇčuun gugha, nomthegha ukur nigha Saiprus…®n m…®ghs…®man gu.
