\v 8 \x - \xo 14:8 \xt Jo 9.1; Ap 3.2\x* Uthughun khav…®n Listran…® uŇčuuna avhen gumaghan mav…®n aŇčgari maghat…®gha am…®rasima aŇčna arui phat…®ghava apheraghav…®re iti. AŇčni inaghamuuŇč aŇčm mbatesima a kamagh…®ra gari.
\v 9 \x - \xo 14:9 \xt Mt 8.10; 9.28-29; Ap 3.4\x* A Pol…® orasima aŇčna akam…® ukuri. Mauthughura Pol r…®k…®rav aŇčn gara kamagha ikaaŇči. Kha gumagh n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar iti. A inderaghami.
\p 
\v 10 Mauthughura Pol kamagh mb…®gh…®rav…®ra deeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® r…®kavigh…® utu!‚ÄĚ Gumaghan khav nomb…® ukunigha utugha magh…®ra arui.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 14:11 \xt Ap 8.10; 28.6\x* Mauthughura gumasi rako amisira avh…®rar kharsi Pol amuisi bighan khav…®n ganigha, mb…®gh…®rav…®ra Likoniana akaman d…®…®gha mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAsae, gumasir m…®n othuivigha em…®usua zaaghire!‚ÄĚ
\v 12 Mauthughura Barnabas, mee asaaŇč Sus…®n aŇčga ath…®. Pol a mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r…® ufhuaragha zui gumagh, kamagh amuisima mee asaaŇč Hermes…®n aŇčga ath…®. \f * \fr 14:12 \ft GrighiiŇčna akamaŇčga aghuuir gumasi rako amisi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar kamagh iti. Asaera avh…®rara ivh…®re iti. Mena asaaŇč mav, Sus, a mena asaer gumaghana aphan. Hermes ivh…®ra mena asaaŇč mav, ana asaera akam nigha zii.\f*
\v 13 AsaaŇč Sus…®n r…®phen, a Listran…® uŇčuun r…®v…®nana ak…®rani iti. Uthughun khav…®n Sus…®n aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumagh, aŇčn phorugha gumasira avh…®rara, mee Pol ri Barnabas…®usua as…®si v…®suegh…®va aniiŇčn aphuraphuraousua. Kamagha amuisi, ana ak…®maria b…®sighava, burmaghari marsi nigha Listran…® uŇčuun r…®v…®nan it…®mana akamaniiŇčn ze.
\p 
\v 14 Mee zesima, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi Pol ri Barnabas, aniiŇč bisir kharsi varaegha, aniiŇč non shaaria b…®gh…®suegha, akh…®ghavt…®gha gumasi iti phogh…®na avhen gua mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi,
\v 15 \x - \xo 14:15 \xt Kis 20.11; 2 Sml 12.21; Sng 33.6; 146.6; Ap 10.26; 1 Ko 8.4; 1 Te 1.9; Je 5.17\x* ‚ÄúMaia! Gumasi, gee thoghousua oth…®vhan khav…® amui? AŇčga ivh…®ra gen m…®n gari, phura gumaghan kh…®nani. AŇčga kamagh…®usua akamana aghuuŇčn gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Gee phura bisir k…®nir kharsir iz…®…®ri ufha thaghri. Gee nori nigh…®va aŇčgam…®re iti Got…® ran…®…®Ňč. A kha ovhee ko unuagh…®n koma oŇčara amuisi Got, andar iti bisi ivh…®rama amuisi God.
\v 16 \x - \xo 14:16 \xt Sng 81.12; Ap 17.30; 1 Pi 4.3\x* Fhom…®ra, Got…®n…® uŇčuimba bar mee thaesima, mee phura non n…®gh…®n…®sira aruava bisigha amui.
\v 17 \x - \xo 14:17 \xt Sng 147.8; Jer 5.24; 14.22; Ap 17.27; Ro 1.20\x* A gen mondusi phat…®. A m…®ghas…®gh…®va othevira aghuuira geŇčga amui. Amogh…®n geŇčga an…®Ňčgava, aghaera aghuuira avh…®rara geŇčga an…®Ňčgava andagha amuima anda othuivi. A geŇčga amuima gen navi inderagh…®v…®ra bari inighinisi.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 AniiŇč bisir kharsir mem mb…®Ňčg…®, akaara aghavagharir mem mb…®Ňčg…®va men th…®va kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee aŇčgagha aphuraphuruva aghae rako bisir aŇčgara an…®…®Ňč thagh…®ri.‚ÄĚ Mee mamagha amuigha aniiŇčga amuisi phat…®.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 14:19 \xt Ap 13.45; 17.13; 2 Ko 11.25; 2 Ti 3.11\x* G…®n Judarir akogh…®n gumasir marsi Antiogh ko Aikoniam…®n ikhegha Listran zegha, mee gumasir n…®gh…®n…®sigh ikuigha meŇčga amuisi, mee Pol…®n aphanaŇčga amui. Mee aŇčg…®r Pol…® inivigha aŇčn ganigha kamagh…®usue, an aremigha g…®va. Mee ana ukurugha Listran…® uŇčuun r…®v…®nan ak…®ran gu.
\v 20 G…®n suren gumasi zaava ana ighuisima, a r…®kavhigha nomthegha Listran…® uŇčuun gu. Am…®r…®tusi a Barnabas…®n phorugha aniiŇč Derben…®n…® uŇčuun zui.
\s1 Pol ri Barnabas…®n suren gumasi gamgaaŇč meŇčga an…®ndi
