\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Mt 28.19\x* Pol ri Barnabas Derben…®n…® uŇčuun ikava akamana aghuuŇč ukurava gumasi rako amisira avh…®rara amuima, mee suren gumasir othuivi. AniiŇč nomthegha Listra ko Aikoniam koma Antiogh…®n ze.
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt Mt 7.14; Ap 11.23; 15.32; 18.23; 1 Te 3.3\x* AniiŇč gamgaaŇčn suren gumasigha aniiŇčgava akuruvasir…® mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r meŇčga amua kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGen non n…®gh…®n…®sir aghavagharir…® utuivigh aghavagharigh…®ri.‚ÄĚ AniiŇč kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGumasi rako amisi Gota ativasi tharsi, ee ivh…®ra mena avh…®ran khav…®na avhen maŇčŇčam…®usua, ee ufhuaragh os…®mnd…®sira avh…®rara niaŇčga.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 \x - \xo 14:23 \xt Ap 13.1-3; 15.40\x* Pol ri Barnabas Krais…®na andarsi itir…® uŇčuimbav…®usua uvhuaghuvhagha Krais…®na andarsir gumasira aphania v…®sevi. Gumasir aruur kharsi non n…®gh…®n…®sira aghavagharir Ikh…®va ath…®gha g…®va. Mauthughura aniiŇč mem…®usua aghae tham…®ragha Ikh…®van phorugha mb…®kemigha bar mee nigha Ikh…®vana afhar…® ath…®.
\s1 Pol ri Barnabas nomthegha Antiogh…®n zui. A Sirian distrigh…®na avhen iti.
