\v 27 \x - \xo 14:27 \xt Ap 11.18; 15.4; 15.12\x* AniiŇč Antiogh…®no otogha, Krais…®na andarsir d…®…®sima mee nori akhuvasima. AniiŇč kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeghi, ‚ÄúGot aŇčgana agharaniiŇčn bisi kharsigha amui. Got ivh…®ra igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasiv…®usua utuava r…®k…®risima, thighira mena marsi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Krais…®n akaman iti.‚ÄĚ
