\c 15
\s1 Krais…®n phorus tharsi Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuun nori akuvaghav iti
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt Wkp 12.3; Jo 7.22; Ga 2.12; 5.2; Kl 2.8; 2.11; 2.16\x* Judian distrigh…®n gumasir marsi Antiogh…®n zegha Krais…®n phorus tharsir surea amua kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee Moses…®no othevir g…®n maŇč…®va non momooŇčn niro ofh…®sia r…®ghorightima Got nomthegh gee niaŇčga. Gee non momooŇčn niro ofh…®sia r…®ghghorighem phat…®ghtima Got nomthegh gee nighem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Ap 11.30; Ga 2.1\x* Kamagha amuisima, Pol ri Barnabas andaran ik…®van men phorughava aŇčga amui. Kamagha amuisima Krais…®n phorusi tharsi Pol ri Barnabas…® mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúEna marsi aŇčgon phorugh Jerusalem…®n maaŇč…®va, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir rako Krais…®n phorusi gumasira aphanir phorugh…®va akaman khava r…®k…®rami.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Mauthughura Krais…®na andarsi mee amandasima Pol ri Barnabas koma Krais…®n phorusi marsi ivh…®ra men phorughava Fonisian distrigh ko Samarian distrigh mogh gu. Mee gua igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®rasi bisir gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Mem mb…®kemisima Krais…®n phorusi tharsi mee bar mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man khav…® oraegha bari inighinisi.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 15:4 \xt Ap 14.27\x* Mauthughura Pol ri Barnabas koma Krais…®n phorus tharsi mee gua Jerusalem…®n othuivi. Mee othuivisima Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir rako Krais…®na andarsi rakoma men gumasira aphani bar vhusvhusigha mee nii. Uthughun khav…®n Pol ri Barnabas Got aniiŇčn afharimuuna amuisi bisi, aniiŇč andar gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 5 Mauthughura FarisiiŇčna akogh…®n gumasir marsi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti tharsi, mee r…®kavhigha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúIgharisir…® unuagh…®nan iti gumasi ivh…®ra Moses os…®risiro othevir g…®n maŇč…®va non momooŇčn niro ofh…®sia r…®ghoromi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi rako Krais…®na andarsir gumasira aphanira akaman khava r…®k…®rousua nori akuvagha iti.
\v 7 \x - \xo 15:7 \xt Ap 10.1-43\x* Uthughun uruaran mee bighan khav…®n mb…®Ňčg…® gugha Pita r…®kavhigha mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNana avheeŇčmbuagha gee ikaaŇči. Got fhom…®ra gen thooŇčn nam mb…®sevigha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėN…®…® igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi nana akaman aghuuŇčn mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man gun mem mb…®k…®mtima mee oraegh n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n ikaami.‚Äô
\v 8 \x - \xo 15:8 \xt 1 Sto 28.9; Ap 1.24; 2.4; 10.44; 11.15\x* Ee ikaaŇči. Got gumasi rako amisir navir averi ikaaŇči. A non…® Utuman igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasigha an…®…®Ňči. A eŇčga amuisi mogh…®ra, a meŇčga amui. A bighan khav…®n en kh…®vagha, a men vhusvhusigha nom mee nii.
\v 9 \x - \xo 15:9 \xt Ap 10.15; 10.28; 10.34-35; Ro 10.11; 1 Ko 1.2; 1 Pi 1.22\x* Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn Judarii rako igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi, ee bar mamagh…®ra gue. Igharsir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n itima, Got men navigha amuisima mee aŇčna ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn…® uzue.
\v 10 \x - \xo 15:10 \xt Mt 11.30; 23.4; Lu 11.46; Ga 3.10; 5.1\x* Moses fhom…®ra os…®risir othevi ena avhavi andar g…®n maŇčŇčan iŇčgurasi tharsi rako othevi ee thighira ivh…®ra andar g…®n maŇčŇčan iŇčguraŇčguraesi tharsi, gee anda nigha n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti tharsir ran…®…®Ňčga. Gee theghousua kamagha amua Got…® ondaaghi?
\v 11 \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Ro 3.24; Ga 2.16; Ef 2.5-8; Ta 2.11\x* En n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėEn Ikh…®v Iesus en…® ukuarkuvisi, Got ena akurasi mogh…®ra mena akuruvaghami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
