\v 12 \x - \xo 15:12 \xt Ap 14.27\x* Uthughun khav…®n gumasi nori akuvasi tharsi bar in…®m…®re ikha Barnabas ri Polr…® orasi. Mee orasima, aniiŇč gamgaaŇčn bisi rako r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuir othevir gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. AniiŇč kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGot aniiŇčn afharir othevir kharsi igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasira ar…®ghana, andagha amui.‚ÄĚ
