\v 20 \x - \xo 15:20 \xt Stt 9.4; Kis 34.15-17; Wkp 17.10-16; 18.6-23; 1 Ko 6.9; 6.18; 8.1; Ga 5.19; Ef 5.3; Kl 3.5; 1 Pi 4.3\x* Ee mem…®usua os…®r…®va kamagh mem mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėGee mee marvir guagha an…®ndir aghaer rama thagh…®ri. Gee anda rameghemi, gee Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn maghatiighemi. Gee nori nigha akuir othevir maghat…®si ramua thagh…®ri. Mee umbuer…® ufh…®ri v…®k…®rima ar…®ghiresi as…®si, andar Ňčae andare iti gee anda rama thagh…®ri. Gee Ňčaana thava rama thagh…®ri.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 15:21 \xt Ap 13.15\x* Gee ikaaŇči. Moses os…®risi oth…®vhan khav, fhom…®ra zaa thighira, mee aŇčna akam uŇčuimbar avhen ana ukuri. Mee avhughususan…® uthughun uthusir m…®ghas…®gha Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phenir avhen aŇč r…®mbori.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Mee igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi Got ikeeŇčsi tharsi mem…®usua mb…®ghara amandi
\p 
\v 22 Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir rako Krais…®na andarsir gumasira aphani koma Jerusalem…®ni iti Krais…®na andarsi mee Jems…®n akaman mb…®nambagha norira ar…®ghan gumaghan mania mb…®sevi, Sailas ri Judas. Judas aŇčn iz…®…®n mav Barsabas. Gumaghan khaniiŇč Krais…®n phorus tharsir ufhuaragha zui. Mee aniiŇč amandasima aniiŇč Pol ri Barnabas…®n phorugha Antiogh…®n zui.
\v 23 AniiŇč mb…®gharan khav nigha zui. Mb…®gharan khav kamagh…®usue.
\p ‚ÄúEe, Iesus…®m mb…®sevisi gumasir rako Krais…®na andarsir gumasira aphani, ee gena andarsi. Ee gem…®usua mb…®gharan khava amandi. Gee igharisir…® unuagh…®nan iti tharsi n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti. Gee Antiogh…®n…® uŇčuun ko Sirian distrigh koma Silisian distrigh…®n iti. Uthughun aghuuŇč.
