\v 29 \x - \xo 15:29 \xt Wkp 17.14; Ap 15.20; 21.25; KTH 2.14; 2.20\x* Gee mee marvir guagha an…®ndir aghaer rama thagh…®ri. Gee anda rameghemi, gee Got…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn maghatiighemi. As…®si mee umbuer…® ufh…®ri v…®k…®rima ar…®ghiresi tharsi, andar Ňčae andare iti gee anda rama thagh…®ri. Gee Ňčaana thava rama thagh…®ri. Gee nori nigha akuir othevir maghat…®si ramua thagh…®ri. Gee bisir kharsi a thaegh inderaghami. En akam kamagh…®rou utu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
