\v 5 \x - \xo 17:5 \xt Ro 16.21\x* Gumasira avh…®rara Pol ri Sailas…®n n…®gh…®n…®ghan g…®n zuima, kamagha amuisima Judarir navi bar men maghat…®ghi. Mee phurama aruava phogh…®n iti gumasir maghat…®sir marsi akumakumigha gumasir b…®san ikh…®va amui. Mee gua uŇčuuni ikh…®vana avhen arua mb…®gh…®rav…®ra avesava aŇčgaravasi. Mee Pol ri Sailas nigh…®va avh…®rar thooŇčn maŇčŇčam…®usua, ith…®makharigha aniiŇčn usuighousuava akh…®r…®siigha Jeson…® r…®phenana avhen gue.
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt Ap 16.20\x* Mee aniiŇčn ganisi phat…®gha, Jeson koma Krais…®n marsi ukuruvaegha uŇčuuni ikh…®van garir gumasir aphaniv…®usua mee nigha gu. Mee kamagh deeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan khaniiŇč os…®mnd…®sir…® unuagh…®nan khav…®n uŇčuimba bar andagha ar…®gha zaa thighira khagho othuivi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 17:7 \xt Lu 23.2; Jo 19.12; 1 Pi 2.13\x* Mauthughura Jesona aniiŇč nigha no r…®phenaŇčga ath…®. Gumaghan khaniiŇč Sisar os…®risir othevir g…®n maŇčŇčan bar iph…®rph…®ri. AniiŇč kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėAtivasir ikh…®van igharisi mav ivh…®re iti, aŇčni iz…®…® Iesus.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 8 Gumasi rako amisira avh…®rara nori akuvasi tharsi koma uŇčuuni ikh…®van garir gumasira aphani, mee men akaman khav…® oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha d…®…® uthuaghii.
\v 9 Mauthughura uŇčuuni ikh…®van garir gumasir aphani kamagh Jeson…®m mb…®kemi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nona andarsira akhuvagh…®va kha os…®m…®nd…®gho ovhesightima, ee gea thaeghtima, gee maŇčŇčaŇčga.‚ÄĚ Mee mamagha amuigha norivagha uvhuesighava nori gue.
\s1 Berian…® uŇčuun iti Judariro oth…®vhan aghuuŇč
\p 
\v 10 Am…®n ph…®rima, Krais…®na andarsi uzuam…®ra aniiŇč amandasi aniiŇč Berian…® uŇčuun gu. AniiŇč gua otogha Judarii Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phenana avhen gu.
\v 11 \x - \xo 17:11 \xt Ais 34.16; Lu 16.29; Jo 5.39\x* Berian…® uŇčuuni itir Judarii, men othevi rako men n…®gh…®n…®si bar indera. Mee Pol…®m mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®va oraghaousua bar vhusvhusi. Mee Pol…®m mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…® v…®n…®Ňčgaria b…®gh…®va bar anda ikaaŇčm…®usua m…®ghas…®gh Got…®m Mb…®gharan ganri. Mee kamagh ikaaŇčm…®usua, Pol…®m mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®, anda guisimbaaŇčra mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®, o? Kamagha amuisima, mee Tesalonaikan…® uŇčuuni iti Judariro othevigha afhira.
\v 12 Judarii avh…®rara n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®ni ikava, ivh…®ra iz…®…®ri iti GrighiiŇčna akamaŇčga aghuuir amisi marsi rako GrighiiŇčna akamaŇčga aghuuir gumasira avh…®rara n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®ni iti.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 17:13 \xt Ap 13.50; 14.19\x* Tesalonaikan…® uŇčuuni iti Judarir akogh…®n gumasir marsi orasi, Pol Berian…® uŇčuuni ikha Got…®na akam…® ukuri. Tesalonaikan…® uŇčua thaegha gua Berian…® uŇčuuni iti Judarii, mee Berian…® uŇčuun gumasi rako amisir kharsi n…®gh…®n…®sira afharavaghava men navighi inivi.
\v 14 Krais…®na andarsi uzuam…®ra Pol amandasi ano oŇčara mb…®keeŇčn gu. Sailas ri Timoti Berian…® uŇčuuni ikhav…®re iti.
\v 15 Uthughun khav…®n Pol…®n akua zuir gumasi gua Atens…®n…® uŇčuun ana ath…®sima, Pol nomb…®n g…®n zaaosua Sailas ri Timotiusua akaman meŇčga an…®…®Ňči.
\s1 Pol Atens…®n…® uŇčuuni ikava akam…® ukuri
\p 
\v 16 Pol Atens…®n…® uŇčuuni ikha Sailas ri Timoti usua gari. A garima, Atens…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®vana avhen marvir gua bar iz…®va. Kamagha amuisi Pol…®n…® umuu bar maghat…®ghi.
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt Ap 18.19\x* A bighan khav…®usua Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phenana avhen gugha, Got…®n apheeŇčni ikava aŇčni iz…®…® ufhuir GrighiiŇčna marsi rako Judarir akogh…®n gumasi ivh…®ra mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A ivh…®ra bisigh…® uvhuesir aŇčanan m…®ghas…®gha gumasi phura zaava othuivi tharsi v…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 18 Uthughun khav…®n Epikurian phogh…®n gumasi rako Stoik…®n phogh…®n ikaaŇčmaran gumasir marsi mee Pol…®n phorugha nori vatosi. Marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúOŇčanan mav tisi v…®Ňčgeeghi?‚ÄĚ Marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúA ti igharisir…® uŇčuun itir asaaniiŇčn akam…® ukuramati.‚ÄĚ Pol Iesus…®n gun…®m mb…®Ňčg…®…®va, gumasi rako amisi gumughuna ar…®ghiregh…®va nomthegh r…®khavamir bighaaŇčn gun…®m mb…®kemisima Atens…®n…® uŇčuuni itir marsi mee kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúA ti kha asaaniiŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®mati.‚ÄĚ
\v 19-20 Mee ana nigha Atens…®n…® uŇčuun garir gumasira aphanir ikiir ar…®ghan guava mee Areopagus…®n oragh…®n nori akuvagha iti. Mee kamagh Pol…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe fhom…®ra thange oraesi phat…®si n…®gh…®n…®si n…®…® anda v…®Ňčgeeghi. Ee anda v…®n…®…®Ňčgari ikaaŇčn vhusvhusi. Kamagha amuisi ee ikaaŇčm…®usua, khara n…®gh…®n…®ghan ikaman mav, n…®…® aŇčn gumasir surea amui. N…®…® khara em mb…®Ňčgeeghi.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 (Atens…®n…® uŇčuun gumasi rakoma Atens…®n…® uŇčuuna ak…®ran zaa iti tharsi, mee m…®ghas…®gha phure ikava n…®gh…®n…®sir iŇčgaava oraghava anda v…®Ňčgeeghi.)
\p 
\v 22 Pol gumasira ar…®ghan…® uthugha Areopagus…®no oragh…®n kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee Atens…®n…® uŇčuun gumasi! Kh…®…® gen garima, gee asaer g…®n maŇčŇčam…®usua bar aghavaghari.
\v 23 Kh…®…® arua bar inderaghav…®ra gen marvir guaar garava, gee asaeghi inighinisi bisi bara andar gani. Kh…®…® ivh…®ra aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndira akhogh…®n mav…®n garima, os…®…®ran mav aŇčni iti. Ma os…®…®r kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėEe ikeeŇčsi phat…®sir asaaŇčna aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir akogh.‚Äô Thighira gee g…®n zuira asaaŇčn khav gee ikeeŇčsi phat…®si thav, kha aŇčna akaman gun gem mb…®k…®mam…®usua.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 17:24 \xt Mt 11.25; Ap 7.48; 14.15\xt 1 Kin 8.27; Ais 42.5\x* AsaaŇč mav iti. AŇčn iz…®…® Got, a nomb…®ra unuagh…®nan khav koma aŇčn iti bisigha amui. Anara ovhee ko unuagh…®nan Ikh…®v. Gumasi nona afharir amuisi r…®pheni Got andar iti phat…®.
\v 25 \x - \xo 17:25 \xt Jop 12.10; Sng 50.12; Sek 12.1; Ap 7.48\x* Got…®n khav a nomb…® ambirambina aghuuŇč ko bisi bar gumasi rako amisigha an…®…®Ňči. A bigha thav…®n othevisi phat…®. Kamagha amuisima, ee nona afharir an akuruvaghamir bigha thav…® ramuighem phat…®ghami.
\v 26 Got gumaghan…® uvhuav…®ra amuisima, gumasi rako amisi bar aŇčno othuivigha gua unuagh…®na khav bar aŇčga aphighi. Got nomb…® mee ikhaamir ambirambin…® uthusi ar…®ghi. Mee itir aŇčanir a mem…®usua unuagh…®n mb…®thee ar…®ghi.
\v 27 \x - \xo 17:27 \xt Lo 32.8; Sng 145.18; Ais 55.6; Jer 23.23; Ap 14.17; Ro 1.20\x* Got…®n vhusvhus a kamagh iti, gumasi rako amisi aŇčm…®usua uruiva, aŇčna aghare ik…®va ana ikeeŇčgemi, kamagha amuisima a kha bisigha amui. GuisimbaaŇčra Got…® uvhuaghuvhagha eni isaghuni iti phat…®.
\v 28-29 \x - \xo 17:28-29 \xt Kl 1.17; Ta 1.12; Hi 1.3\xt Ais 40.18-20; 44.10-17; Ap 19.26\x* Anara eŇčga amuima, ee ikava, aruava aŇčam…®re iti. Geni ikaaŇčmarir gumasir marsi kamagh…®m mb…®kemi, ‚ÄėGot guisimbaaŇčra enga amuisima ee othuivi.‚Äô Kamagha amuisima gee kamagh n…®gh…®n…®gha thagh…®ri, Got a gol o silva o ak…®m ti. Ee kamagh n…®gh…®n…®gha thagh…®ri, Got a gumasi nona n…®gh…®n…®sir amuisir marvir guaar m…®n iti bar phat…®.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 17:30 \xt Ap 14.16; Ro 3.25; Ta 2.11-12; 1 Pi 1.14\x* Fhom…®ra gumasi rako amisi Got ikeeŇčsi phat…®. Mee ikeeŇčsi phat…®ghava amuisi bisi Got andagh…® n…®gh…®n…®gha andavagha mem mb…®Ňčgee phat…®. Thighira Got…® mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man aghavaghara an…®…®Ňčga kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėUnuagh…®na khav…®n iti gumasi rako amisi mee bar non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®ragh…®ri.‚Äô
\v 31 \x - \xo 17:31 \xt Sng 9.8; 96.13; Ap 2.24; 10.42; Ro 2.16; 14.10\x* Got othevir maghat…®sigha amuir gumasi rako amisighi ighaaŇčgamir…® utugha r…®k…®righa g…®va. Got nono oth…®vhan aghuuŇčn g…®n gua gumaghan mavam mb…®sevi. Ma gumagh a unuagh…®nan khav…®n iti gumasi rako amisighi ighaaŇčgami. Gumaghan khav aremisi Got aŇčga amuisima a nomthegha r…®kavi. Kamagha amuisima, gumasi rako amisi ganighava ikaaŇči. Kha bighaaŇč anaaŇč guisimbaaŇčra, a gumasi rako amisighi ighaaŇčgamir gumagh Got anam mb…®sevi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Am mb…®Ňčgeema, mee nom…® r…®kavamir…® mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®v oraegha, marsi aŇč r…®phovi. Marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® uthugh thav…®n nomthegh…®va bighan khav…®m mb…®k…®mti, ee n…®…®m mbaraghaousua.‚ÄĚ
\v 33 Mauthughura Pol mea thaegha gu.
\v 34 Gumasir marsi Pol…®n n…®gh…®n…®ghan g…®n gua n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r iti. Men thooŇčn Dionisius a gumaghana aphanan mav m…®ghas…®gha men phorugha Areopagus…®n oragh…®n phosir…® usuisir gumagh. Amighan mav ivh…®ra, aŇčni iz…®…® Damaris, koma gumasi rako amisir marsi ivh…®ra mee n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Pol…®n mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r iti.
\c 18
\s1 Pol Korin…® uŇčuun Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč ukuri
\p 
\v 1 Bisi kharsir g…®n, Pol Atens…®n…® uŇčua thaegha Korin…®n…® uŇčuun gu.
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Ro 16.3; 1 Ko 16.19; 2 Ti 4.19\x* A khagh Judarir akogh…®n gumaghan mav…® oto, aŇčni iz…®…® Akwila. AŇčn…® uŇčuu Pontus…®n distrigh…®na avheni iti. A nona amuuŇč Prisilana akua Italin…® unuagh…®nan ik…®ran uruaraaŇčra mange itima, uthughun khav…®n Sisar, aŇčni iz…®…®n mav Klodius a Judarii v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee Rom…®n…® uŇčuuni ik…®va thaegh igharagh maaŇč…®ri.‚ÄĚ Kamagha amuigha, aniiŇč Italin…® unuagh…®na thaegha Korin…® uŇčuun ze. Uthughun khav…®n Pol aniiŇčn ganam…®usua zui.
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Ap 20.34; 1 Ko 4.12; 1 Te 2.9; 2 Te 3.8\x* Pol ivh…®ra aniiŇčn m…®ra, seli r…®phenigha amui. Kamagha amuisima, ana aniiŇčn ganam…®usua gua, aniiŇčn aghan ikava men phorugha iŇčaari.
\v 4 Avhughususan…® uthusir, Pol m…®ghas…®gha Judarii Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phenir gua men phorugha mee nori v…®Ňčgeeghi. A Judarii rako GrighiiŇčna akamaŇčga aghuuir gumasi rako amisi, men n…®gh…®n…®sir ramutima, mee n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n ikhaousua meŇčga aghori.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt Ap 9.22; 17.3; 17.14-15; 18.28\x* Mauthughura Sailas ri Timoti Masedonian distrigha thaegha zesima, Pol bar non…® uthusir m…®ghas…®gha Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč ukuri. AŇčna akaman aghavagharan Judarii inderaghav…®ra kamagh meŇčgi ighari, Iesus, a Got nom gumasi rakoma amisi niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh.
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Ese 18.13; Ap 13.45-46; 13.51; 20.26; 1 Pi 4.4\x* Uthughun khav…®n Judarii Pol…®n akamam mbaraghan agharkuvighava, mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r maghat…®sir aŇčga amui. Mee kamagh amuisima, a non shaaran mb…®nisi aph…®sigha, kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee kamagh Got…®n isaghun ik…®…®va nori ar…®m…®ghi iraami, mara gen os…®mnd…®ghara. Kh…®…® nomb…® os…®mnd…®si phat…®. Thighira kh…®…® Got…®na akamana aghuuŇčn igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi v…®k…®maŇčga.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Mauthughura Pol Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phena thaegha Titius…® r…®phenan gu. AŇčn iz…®…®n mav Jastus, gumaghan khav m…®ghas…®gha Got…®n apheeŇčn ikava aŇčni iz…®…® ufhii. AŇč r…®phen a Judarii Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phenan aghan iti.
\v 8 \x - \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Ko 1.14\x* Krispus, Judarir Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phenan bisir garir gumagh. A nona andarsir phorugha mee n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Ikh…®van iti. Uthughun khav…®n Korin…® uŇčuun gumasi rako amisira avh…®rara Pol…®n akamam mbaraegha n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®n itima mee mee urue.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Ap 23.11; 1 Ko 2.3\x* R…®maaŇčn mav…®n, Ikh…®v ir…®m…®n m…®n bighan Pol…® mb…®kemi, ‚ÄúN…®…® avhighavigha thagh…®ri. N…®…® mb…®k…®mv…®re ikh…®…®. In…®m…®re ikaa thagh…®ri.
\v 10 \x - \xo 18:10 \xt Jos 1.9; Ais 41.10; Jer 1.8; 1.18-19; Mt 28.20; Jo 10.16\x* Kh…®…® n…®…® phorugha iti, nan gumasi rako amisira avh…®rara uŇčuuni ikh…®van khav…®ni iti. Kamagha amuisi thav iphas n…®…® ramuva, n…®…® mb…®sueghem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Gumughun Pol ombaran…® uvhuav…®ra koma mav…®no ofh…®ghaaŇčn ikava, Got…®na akamana aghuuŇčn men surea amui.
\p 
\v 12 Galio, Akaian distrigh…®n gavman…®n gumaghana aphanan itima, Judarir akogh…®n gumasi bar r…®kavhigha Pol…®n aphanaŇčga amuava ana nigha os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir aŇčanana arogh…®a ath…®.
\v 13 Mee kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGumaghan khav, a gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėGee Moses os…®risir othevi r…®kaphogh…®va, oth…®vhan igharis thav…®n Got…®n apheeŇčn ikava aŇčni iz…®…® ufhii.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\v 14 \x - \xo 18:14 \xt Ap 23.29; 25.11; 25.19\x* Pol bar mena akam ikaravaghaousuava amuima, Galio Judarii v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan khav RomiiŇč os…®risir othevia biighemi, o aŇčno oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav…® ramuightima, kh…®…® Judarii gena akaav oraghami.
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Jo 18.31; Ap 23.29; 25.18-19\x* Geem mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r othevi rako atamatam iz…®…®ri rakoma gen othevi, andagh…® n…®gh…®n…®gha nam…®usua zaa thagh…®ri. Gee nori andar r…®k…®righ…®ri. Kh…®…® bisir kharsiro os…®mnd…®si varaeghem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 Kamagha amuisima a mee amandasima mee ana thaegha ze.
\v 17 Uthughun khav…®n Korin…® uŇčuun gumasi, Sostenes…®n…® usuiragha, os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir aŇčanana arogh…®m mb…®keeŇčn aŇčm mb…®sosi. A Judarii Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phenan bisir garir gumagh. Mauthughura Galion n…®gh…®n…®gh a kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúMe mara aŇčra amu.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pol nomthegha Antiogh…®n…® uŇčuun zii
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 18:18 \xt Nam 6.18; Ap 21.24; Ro 16.1\x* Pol…® uthusir marsir Korin…® uŇčuuni ikhegha, Prisila ri Akwila nigha, mee Krais…®na andarsia thaegha zaava Senkrian…® uŇčuuno othuivighava, a nona akama r…®ng…®ra g…®vagha nona aphanana ar…®gh…®na r…®ph…®ri. Kamagha amuigha g…®vagha mee Sirian distrigh…®n zaaousuava ukuran guava anambogha nori zii.
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt Ap 17.17\x* Mee Efesus…®n…® uŇčuuno othuivigha, Pol a Prisila ri Akwila anamogha aniiŇč thaghi. A nomb…® Judarir Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgee r…®phena mav…®n gua men phorugha nori v…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 20 Mee uthusi tharsir norir gan ikhaaousuava aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeema, a kamagh…®usue, phat…®.
\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Ro 1.10; 1 Ko 4.19; Hi 6.3; Je 4.15\x* A mauthughura a mea tham…®ragha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGot vhusvhusightima, kh…®…® nomthegh gem…®usua zaami.‚ÄĚ A kamagh…®m mb…®kemigha ukur nigha Efesus…®n…® uŇčua thaegha ze.
\v 22 A Sirian distrigh…®n zaava Sisarian…® uŇčuuno otogha, Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuun iti Krais…®na andarsighi itiisua zaavanambogha g…®n Antiogh…®n…® uŇčuun zeghir…®.
\p 
\v 23 Gumughun Pol uthusir marsi Antiogh…®n…® uŇčuuni ikhegha, a Galesian distrigh koma Frigian distrigh…®ni itir…® uŇčuimba bar andagha aruava, n…®gh…®n…®ghan aghavaghar Iesus…®n iti tharsi a gamgaaŇč meŇčga an…®ndi.
\s1 Apolos Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč Efesus…®n…® uŇčuun ana ukuri
\p 
