\v 10 \x - \xo 26:10 \xt Ap 9.14; 9.21; Ga 1.13\x* Kh…®…® bisir kharsi Jerusalem…®n andagha amui. Kh…®…® Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikii andar gamgaaŇč nigha, kh…®…® Got…®n gumasi rako amisi mena avh…®rara nigha r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®ghan mee ar…®ghi. Uthughun khav…®n gumasira aphani mem mb…®soghtima mee aremighaousuava mem mb…®Ňčgeema, kh…®…® ivh…®ra kamagh…®usue, mee ar…®m…®ghiregh…®ri.
\v 11 Uthusira avh…®rara kh…®…® Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeer r…®phenigha aruava andara avhen gua, men…® usuigha mem mb…®sosi. Kh…®…® ambaragh mee ramutima mee akaar maghat…®sir Ikh…®vam mb…®k…®m…®va aŇčni iz…®…®ra afharavaghami. Nan nav mem…®usua phuv…®ra nan sima kh…®…® isaghuni iti uŇčuimbar gua mera afaravaghasoua mamem…®usua uri.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pol Krais…®n…® andarsira mbaaŇčn niazi
\r (Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi 9.3-19 koma Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi 22.6-16)
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 26:12 \xt Ap 9.3; 22.6\x* Pol mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúUthughun mav…®n, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndi gumasiri ikiira, mee akamana aghavagharan naŇčga an…®…®Ňčgava, mee na amandasima kh…®…® Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®van zui.
\v 13 O ativasir gumagh, uthugh kamagh 12 oklogh…®n zuima, kh…®…® utuav…®n gua, garima, aŇčaran mav Got…®n uŇčuuni ikhegha zaa naŇčgi isira, aŇčaran khav bara aghavagharigha arona aŇčara afhira. Nan phorughava arui tharsi aŇčaran khav bar eŇčgi isira.
\v 14 Kamagha amuisima ee bar…® unuagh…®n aŇčgi iree, kh…®…® orasima ith…®…®Ňčn mav HibruiiŇčna akaman kamagh nam mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėSol, Sol, n…®…® manmagh…®usuav…®ra nara afharavaghav…®re iti? N…®…® nara afharavasi phat…®, n…®…® mb…®zagh…®n nomb…®ra nomb…®a an…®ndi.‚Äô
\v 15 Mauthughura kha aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄėIkh…®v, n…®…® th…®…®Ňčra?‚Äô Kh…®…® mb…®Ňčgeema Ikh…®v na ikara, ‚ÄėKh…®…® Iesus, n…®…® nara afaravasi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 26:16 \xt Ap 22.15\x* N…®…® r…®kavigh uthuu. Kh…®…® thighira noni iŇčaariv…®usua niam mb…®s…®vaousuava n…®mba oto. N…®…® thighira ganisi bisi rako, kh…®…® g…®n n…®…®n kh…®vamir bisi na andara akam…® ukunaŇčga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 26:17 \xt Ap 22.21\x* Kh…®…® n…®…®a amandaghtima igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi rakoma, Judarir akhogh…®n gumasi rako amisi mee iphas n…®…® ramutima, kh…®…® n…®…®n gan…®va n…®…®na akuruvaghtima, mee n…®ra afharavaeghem phat…®ghami.
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Ais 35.5; 42.7; 42.16; Jo 8.12; Ap 20.32; 2 Ko 6.14; Ef 2.2; Kl 1.13\x* N…®…® kamagh…®rara ramuigh…®va n…®…® mena ar…®masi osemseghtima, mee ak…®r…® …®ragh…®va g…®ng…®nan itira othevir maghat…®sigha asegh…®va, aŇčaran zaami. Mee Satan…®n gamgaaŇč athaegh…®va, Got…®usua zaami. Mee kamagh…® ramuightima kh…®…® meno othevir maghat…®si g…®na amaaŇčga, mee ivh…®ra n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar nani iti gumasi rako amisir ar…®ghan aŇčan niaŇčga. Nan gumasi rako amisir kharsi, mee n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar nan itima, kh…®…® meŇčga amuisima mee uzue. N…®…® iŇčaaran khav…® ramuam…®usua, kh…®…® mem…®usua n…®…®a amandi.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pol noni iŇčaaran gun Agripa mb…®Ňčgeeghi
\p 
\v 19 Arama Pol mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAtivasi gumagh Agripa, kh…®…® Got…®n…® uŇčuuni ikhegha zesi bighan mav…®n ganigha aŇčg…® ph…®rph…®rsi phat…®, kha aŇčna akaman g…®n zui.
\v 20 \x - \xo 26:20 \xt Mt 3.8; Ap 9.20; 9.28-29; 11.26; 13.14\x* Kh…®…® ufhuaragha Damaskus…®n…® uŇčuuna akam…® ukunigha, Jerusalem…®na akam…® ukunigha, Judian distrigh…®n itira aŇčaani bara andara akam…® ukurava, ivh…®ra kh…®…® igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasi rako amisiv…®usua guava akam…® ukurava, kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėGen non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®ragh…®va nomthegh Got…®usua z…®…®. Gee amuiro othevi, gumasi andar gan…®va ikeeŇčg…®m mb…®k…®maŇčŇčga gee non n…®gh…®n…®sigh …®ragha g…®va.‚Äô
\v 21 \x - \xo 26:21 \xt Ap 21.30-31\x* Kh…®…® bisir kharsira akam…® ukurima, mee Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®n nan…® usuira. Uthughun khav…®n Judarii na mb…®suesima kh…®…® ar…®mam…®usuav…®rama amui.
\v 22 \x - \xo 26:22 \xt Lu 24.27; 24.44; Jo 5.46; Ro 3.21\x* Got nana akurasima kh…®…® inderaghav…®re ikha zaa thighira, kh…®…® khagh…® utughava akaman gumasir k…®ni rako gumasir ikii bar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Akaman khav…®ra, Moses ri Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumasi fhom…®ra aŇčn gun…® mb…®kemi. Kh…®…® nomthegha akaman igharisi thav…® ukuri phat…®.
\v 23 \x - \xo 26:23 \xt Ais 42.6; 49.6; Lu 24.26; 24.44-47; 1 Ko 15.20; Kl 1.18\x* Mee kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėGot nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh, Krais aŇčm mb…®zagh nigh…®va aremigh…®va, a ufhuaragh…®v…®ra r…®khavighemi gumagh magh…®. A Got…®n aŇčaran Judarir akogh…®n gumasi rako igharisir…® unuagh…®nan gumasir kh…®vami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ
\s1 Pol n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®n ikhaousuava Agripa mb…®Ňčgeeghi
\p 
\v 24 Pol akam…® ukurav…®re itima, Festus akaman ikh…®van kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúPol, n…®…® oŇčani! N…®…® surera avh…®rara amuisima n…®…®ni ikaaŇčmaran ikh…®v, n…®…®Ňčga amuisima n…®…® oŇčani!‚ÄĚ
\v 25 Pol kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan ikh…®v Festus, kh…®…® oŇčanisi phat…®, kh…®…® guisimbaaŇčram mb…®Ňčgeeghi, kh…®…® n…®gh…®n…®gh ikava kh…®…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 26 \x - \xo 26:26 \xt Jo 18.20\x* Ativasi gumagh Agripa bisir kharsi bar anda ikaaŇči, anda mondughava otuivisi phat…®, kh…®…® ikaaŇči, a ti bisir kharsiv oraghava, andar garava arama anda ikheeŇčgamati. Kamagh amuisima kh…®…® atiti phat…®gha, bar andar gun ativasi gumagh Agripa mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
\v 27 Ativasi gumagh Agripa, n…®…® n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®na ambuuŇčn gumasir iti, o phat…®? Kh…®…® ikaaŇči, n…®…® n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar iti.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Agripa kamagh Pol…®n azara, ‚ÄúManmagha amui, n…®…® kha uthughun oth…®vanŇčra nam mb…®k…®m…®tima kh…®…® manmagh…®ra Krais…®n g…®n maŇč…® ti?‚ÄĚ
\v 29 Ana aŇčm mb…®kemisima Pol ana ikara, ‚ÄúUthughun oth…®va thav o uthughun…® uruara thav, kh…®…® kamagh Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®maŇčga, n…®…® koma kheeŇča, gee thighira nana akamam mbaraghi, gee bar nan m…®no othuivhami. Bighan…® uvhuav…®ra, mee ukuaghaviir gee ikegh…®va gee nigh r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®ghan gee rar…®ghan, kh…®…® iph…®rph…®ri.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Mauthughura ativasi gumasi rako gavman…®n gumasir aphan koma Bernaisin phorugha ikesi tharsi, mee bar r…®kavighava
\v 31 \x - \xo 26:31 \xt Ap 23.9; 23.29; 25.25\x* r…®phena thaegha gugha norira nori v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGumaghan khav oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav…® ramuigh…®va, ana aremighemi, o a r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan ikaami. AŇčno oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav…® amuisi phat…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 32 \x - \xo 26:32 \xt Ap 25.11\x* Mauthughura Agripa kamagh Festus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúA nomb…®ra kamagh…®usue, Sisar nana os…®mnd…®siva oragh…®va anda r…®k…®rami. A ti kamagh…® mb…®kemis phat…®ghav khasima, ee thighira ana thesima ana ak…®ran guaghi.‚ÄĚ
\c 27
\ms1 Pol Rom…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®van zui
\mr (Sapta 27-28)
\s1 Mee Pol nigha gua ukura ath…®sima a Rom…®n zui
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 27:1 \xt Ap 25.12; 25.25\x* Mee, ee nigh Italin…® unuagh…®nan maŇčŇčam…®usuava ukuran phorugha akama r…®k…®righa g…®vaghava, Pol…®n phorugha r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghan iti tharsi ivh…®ra mee nigha 100 plam mb…®zorsir gumasira aphanan afhar…® ath…®, aŇčni iz…®…® Julius, ana ativasi gumaghan garava ana araavi gumasiri ik…®v. \f * \fr 27:1 \ft Pol Jerusalem…®n zima, Luk ti ivh…®ra aŇčn phorugha zui. N…®…® Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasir IŇčaarir…®m Mb…®ghar 16.10 koma 21.17…®n gan. Pol Judian distrigha thaegha RomiiŇčn zuima, Luk ti ivh…®ra aŇčn phorugha gu.\f*
\v 2 \x - \xo 27:2 \xt Ap 19.29\x* Mee ee nigha guava Adramitium…®n…® uŇčuun…® ukura ath…®…®. Ukuran khav Esian distrigh…®n itir…® uŇčuimba v…®keeŇč maŇčŇčam…®usuava amuima, ee magh…®ra aŇčn zui. Mauthughura Aristarkus, a Masedonian distrigh…®n itir…® uŇčuu Tesalonaikan gumagh, a ivh…®ra en phorugha iti.
\v 3 \x - \xo 27:3 \xt Ap 24.23\x* Am…®r…®tusi r…®maaŇčra ee Saidon…®n…® uŇčuuno othuivi. Julius oth…®vhana aghuuŇčn Pol…® amuava ana thaesima a nona andarsiv…®usua zuima, mee aghae rako bisir aŇčna akuruvasi.
\v 4 Ee Saidon…®n…® uŇčuuni ikhegha nomthegha zuima gamiiŇč bar aghavagharisima, kamagha amuisima ee Saiprus…®n m…®ghs…®man gamiiŇč am…®rasira aŇčanan zui.
\v 5 Ee guava Silisian distrigh koma Pamfilian distrigh…®n itira oŇčarani ikh…®va biigha guava Lisian distrigh…®na avhen itir…® uŇčuun ik…®v Mairana oto.
\v 6 Mb…®zorsir gumasir garir gumaghan khav ana Aleksandrian uŇčuun itir…® ukuran garima a Italin…® unuagh…®nan maŇčŇčam…®usuava amuima, an aŇčn ganigha ee nigha guava en aŇčga ath…®.
\v 7 Ee r…®khavighava bar am…®ragh…®v…®ra zuima uthusir marsi g…®va, ukur…® uvhuarira ak…®r…®s…®si phat…®, gamiiŇčni ikh…®v…® r…®kavhisima, ukuram mb…®s…®man…® usuisi gumasi mee iŇčaaran ikh…®vara amua gua ee Nidus…®na aghan zui. Ee zuima gamiiŇč aghavagharigha en…® utuava ph…®risima ee maaŇčan iŇčgura, kamagh amuisima ukur non…® utuava thaegha gua Krit…®n m…®ghs…®mano otogha guava, Salmon…®n…® unuagh…®nano oth…®vhan iti. Uthughun khav…®n ee Krit…®n gamiiŇč uvhuee phat…®sira aŇčanan gueghiri.
\v 8 GamiiŇč bar am…®rasima, mee fhighav…®re iŇčaara gua oŇčarana ataaŇčna anaŇčga zaava aŇčanan mav…®o oto, aŇčanan khav…®n iz…®…® IfhanaaŇčna AghuuŇč ee aŇčmba othuvi. AŇčanan khav a Lasean…® uŇčuuna aghani iti.
\p 
\v 9 Uthusira avh…®rara phura g…®va. Kamagha amuisi Judarir akogh…®n gumasi mee aghae tham…®rasir…® uthugh\f * \fr 27:9 \ft Uthughun ikh…®van khav, Got gumasi rako amisir othevir maghat…®si anda g…®n amandir…® uthugh. N…®…® ikaaŇčm…®usua, Wok Pris 23.26-32…®n gan. Judarir akogh…®n gumasi mee aghae tham…®rasir…® uthughun khav mara gaeŇčmbari ikii Mediterenian oŇčar r…®khavima ukuri arui phat…®.\f* otogha g…®va. Kha uthughun oŇčar bar maghatisima, kamagh amuisima Pol kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi,
\v 10 \x - \xo 27:10 \xt Ap 27.22\x* ‚ÄúGumasi, kh…®…® kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si, ee thighira maŇč…®va uthughun maghat…®gha thav…®o otoghtima ukuran iti bisira avh…®rara mareireghtima, ukur mareireghtima, ee ivh…®ra marereghemi.‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Mb…®zorsir gumasir garir gumagh Pol…®na akamamba oraesi phat…®ghava ukuran guav koma an…® usuisir gumagh aniiŇčn n…®gh…®n…®ghan g…®n zui.
\v 12 IfhanaaŇčn khav a ikh…®va geeŇčmbar ikiir mondugh ikhamiri ifhanaaŇčna aghuuŇč phat…®. Mamagha amuigha ukurani iti gumasira avh…®rara maŇčŇčam…®usuava akama r…®k…®ri. Mee thugharat…®gh…®va mee maŇčŇč…®va Finiks…®n…® uŇčuuno otuivigh…®va kha gamiiŇčn ikh…®van gan kha uŇčuun ikaami. Finiks a ifhanaaŇč mav a Krit…®n m…®ghs…®man saut…® r…®fhaaŇčn itima ukur aro gueghiri r…®fhaaŇč mogh zui.
\s1 GamiiŇčn ikh…®v koma oŇčar r…®kavi
\p 
\v 13 Saut…®n gamiiŇčna am…®…®Ňčnd…®gh…® r…®kavhi. Mee kamagh…®usue, mee ti inderaghav…®ra maaŇč…® Finiks…®n ifhanaaŇčno otuivighemi. Mee kamagh mb…®kemigha ukura asigharafhaghava Krit…®no oŇčara mb…®keeŇčn zui.
\v 14-15 Mee muaŇč ikesima gamiiŇčn bar aghavaghar r…®kavhigha oŇčara amuima a phuv…®ra iŇčaari. Mee kamagh gamiiŇčn khav…® r…®mbori, ‚ÄúNot ko Ist…®n thighiiŇčn r…®kavir gamiiŇč.‚ÄĚ A Krit…®n m…®ghs…®man muaaŇčmogh zaava fighav…®ra ukuro uvhuava ana munamandi. GamiiŇč bar aghavagharisi ukuran iŇčaarir gumasi ukuran…® usuisi phat…®gha ukura thaesi gamiiŇč aŇčgu uvhueema a phura zui.
\v 16 Ee gua Kaudan m…®ghs…®ma mb…®keeŇčn gue. M…®ghs…®man gamiiŇč mange ana aph…®risima ee akeman sovange ikuigha ukuran aghan zaaousua bar iŇčaaran ikh…®va amui.
\v 17 Uthughun khav…®n…® ukuran iŇčaarir gumasi akeman sovange ufhuegha iph…®a ath…®gha, mee umbue ukurima anda guava ukurana apheeŇč guesima, mee ukuran phorugha ane ikesima a bar aghavaghari. Mee maaŇč…® Afrikan oŇčarana ataaŇčn iti g…®r…®r…®Ňčn mavanaŇčna avhighaviigha, ukuran sel…® ukunisi gamiiŇč ukura s…®vaghs…®vasima a zui.
\v 18 GamiiŇč koma oŇčar ivh…®ra bar aghavagharigha phuv…®ra em mb…®sosi. Am…®r…®tusi r…®maaŇčra ukuran iŇčaarir gumasi ukurana avhen iti bisi nigha oŇčarana anda ukuri.
\v 19 Uthughun…® mb…®ketav…®n…® mee ukuaruvan ik…®v nigha magh…®ra ukuran pul…®a amui phuri rako bisir marsi ivh…®rama anda ukuri. Mee nona afharir anda niava anda ukuri. \f * \fr 27:19 \ft GrighiiŇčna akam inderaghav…®ra bighan khav…®n aŇčm mb…®kemisi phat…®.\f*
\v 20 Mauthughura uthusira avh…®rara ee aro koma mb…®kovir ganis phat…®. Uthughun khav…®n gamiiŇč mb…®gh…®rav…®ra eŇčg…® uvhuav…®re iti. Kamagha amuisi ee bar ambuun norira akuragh mb…®gh…®v…®gh…®ghan n…®gh…®n…®gha thav eni iti phat…®.
\p 
\v 21 Uthughun…® uruaraaŇčn gumasi aghaa thava amesi phat…®sima, Pol r…®kavhigha men mb…®n…®man…® utugha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumasi, gee nana akamamba oraegha, ee Krit…®n m…®ghs…®mare ikheghavikhasi uthughun maghat…®ghan khav emba otoghom phat…®ghtima, bisi tharsi mareregham phat…®ghami.
\v 22 \x - \xo 27:22 \xt Ap 27.10; 27.31\x* Kh…®…® thighira gem mb…®k…®mam…®usua, ena thav aremighem phat…®ghami. Kamagha amuisi gee avhighavigha thagh…®ri, gee phura in…®m…®re ikh…®…®. Kamagha amuisima, ena thav marer…®gham phat…®ghtima ukur nomb…®ra marer…®ghami.
\v 23 \x - \xo 27:23 \xt Dan 6.16; Ap 23.11; Ro 1.9\x* Kh…®…® Got…®n gumagh, kh…®…® aŇčni iz…®…® ufhii. R…®maaŇčn Got…®n ensel zaa nana aghan…® utugha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi,
\v 24 \x - \xo 27:24 \xt Ap 23.11\x* ‚ÄėPol, n…®…® avhighavigha thagh…®ri. N…®…® maŇčŇč…®va, Sisar…®na ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn…® utuivami. N…®…® oragh, Got n…®…®na azaaŇčs…®gha oraegha g…®vagha n…®…®n…® ukuarukuvi. N…®…®n phorugha ukuran iti gumasi, mee aremighem phat…®ghami.‚Äô
\v 25 \x - \xo 27:25 \xt Ro 4.20-21; 2 Ti 1.12\x* Gumasi, gee oragh! Kh…®…® n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®n ikha kamagh ikaaŇči, Got nam mb…®kemisi mogh…®ra bisi othuivhami. Kamagh…®n…®, gee gamgaeŇčgiri avhighavigha thagh…®ri.
\v 26 \x - \xo 27:26 \xt Ap 28.1\x* Ee ukura thaeghtima a mara maaŇč…®tima, gamiiŇč aŇčgu uvhu…®rah…®va ana nigh maaŇč…® m…®ghs…®ma thav…®n ana phorughami.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 14 p…®la r…®maŇčgarir gamiiŇč eŇčgu uvhurasima ee Mediterenian oŇčarani ikh…®van iph…®n zui. R…®maaŇčna ar…®gha aghangera zesima ukuran iŇčaarir gumasi n…®gh…®n…®si, ‚ÄúEe unuagh…®nan aghan zaamati.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Kamagha amuisi mee oŇčaran…® ukhond…®ghi ikaaŇčm…®usua umbueeŇč ukunisi a gueghir…®. Kha uthughun oŇčaran…® ukhond…®gh 40 mitan utu. Ukur muaŇč s…®vagha gusima, mee oŇčarana ambarima a 30 mitan…® utu.
\v 29 Mee kamagh avhighavighi, ukur maaŇč…® aŇčg…®…® tharsi itira aŇčanan phorugh bar…®m mb…®sarighireghemi. Mee aŇčkarir 4 p…®la ukuran g…®raŇčg…®rana anda ukunigha, aro anaaŇčm…®usuava nori Got…®n phorugha mb…®Ňčgeeghi.
